hadiths[242]{hadithnumber,text}:
4100,"Hazrat Abu-Zar Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : duniya sey be-raghbati (dilchaspi na hona) halal ko haram karney ya maal zaya karney sey nahin hoti. duniya sey be-raghbati ka matlab ye hai ke tujhey apney paas mojud chiz par Allah key paas mojud chizon sey ziyada aitimad na ho. aur tujh par jo musibat aaye to uskey sawab ki ziyada raghbat (dilchaspi) rakhta ho, ke wo (duniya mein aaney ki bajaey aakhirat mein pesh aaney key liye) terey liye baqi rahey. Abu-Idrees Kholani (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : ye hadees dusri hadeeson key muqabley mein aisi hai jaisey aam soney key muqabley mein khalis (baaees qeeraat key meyaar ka) sona."
4101,"Hazrat Abu-Khallad (Abdur-Rehman bin Zuhair) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum kisi aadmi ko dekho ke usey duniya sey be-raghbati (dilchaspi na ho) aur kam-goi di gaee hai to us sey qarib huwa karo kyonkey wo hikmat ki baaten karta hai."
4102,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey aisa amal bataaiye ke jab main wo karun to Allah mujh sey mohabbat karey aur log mujhey pasand karen. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : duniya sey be-raghbat ho jao , Allah tum sey mohabbat kerega. aur logon key paas jo kuchh hai us sey be-niyaz ho jaao, log tum sey mohabbat kerengey."
4103,"Hazrat Samura bin Saham (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Hazrat Abu-Hashim Khalid bin Utba (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa, jab wo (neze sey) zakhmi ho gaey they. Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) un ki iyaadat ko tashrif laye to Abu-Hashim (Raziallahu anhu) ro padey. Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mamu jaan ! aap kyon rotey hain? kya dard ziyada pareshan kar raha hai ya duniya (key chhutney) par ghamgin hain, is (zindagi) ka umda hissa to guzar gaya? (ab to nikamma hissa hi baqi hai jis mein dukh takleefen ziyada hoti hain). Hazrat Abu-Hashim (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : in mein sey kisi baat par nahin. lekin Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey eik wada liya tha, kaash! main uskey mutabiq chala hota. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : shayad tum ko bahut amwaal milen jo logon mein taqseem kiye ja rahey hon (un ka lalach na karna). tumharey liye to is mein sey eik khaadim aur eik sawari ka janwer Allah ki raah mein (jihad karney key liye) kaafi hai. mujhey maal mila aur mainey jama kar liya."
4104,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat Salman Faarsi (Raziallahu anhu) bimar ho gaey. Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) un ki iyaadat key liye gaey to dekha ke wo ro rahey hain. Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : bhai jaan ! aap kyon ro rahey hain? kya aap Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath nahin rahey? kya aap ney falan kaam nahin kiya? falan kaarnama anjam nahin diya? Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main do chizon mein sey kisi eik par bhi nahin ro raha. main na duniya key chhutney ki wajeh sey rotaa hun, na aakhirat ko napasand kartey huye. lekin (main isliye ro raha hun ke) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey eik wada liya tha. aur main samajhta hun ke mainey us sey tajawuz kya hai (khilaaf-warzi karna). unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aap sey kya wada liya tha? farmaya : aap ney mujh sey farmaya tha : aadmi ko itna kuchh kafi hota hai jitna musafir ka zaade-raah. aur mujhey yaqin hai ke main (us) had sey tajawuz kar (badh) gaya hun. aur aey Saad ! aap jab (kisi jhagdey ka) faisla karen to apney faisley mein Allah ka khof peshe-nazar rakhen. aur jab (mustahiqeen mein koi chiz) taqseem karen to taqseem key waqt (taqwe ko malhooz rakhen). aur jab aap (kisi program key barey mein) sochen (ya irada karen) to apni soch mein (aur iradey mein Allah sey daren). Hazrat Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : mujhey malum huwa ke unhoney tarkey mein sirf taqriban bees Dinar chhodey jo unkey zaati kharchey key liye they."
4105,"Hazrat Aban bin Usman (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) dophare key waqt Marwan (Rahimahullah) key paas sey bahar nikley. mainey kaha : unhoney us waqt unhein koi (aham) masla daryaft karney hi key liye bulaya hoga. mainey Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha to unhoney kaha : unhoney hum sey kuchh hadeeson key barey mein daryaft kiya tha (ke wo kis tarah hain). jo hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suni thin. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : jis shakhs ka maqsud husoole duniya ho, Allah Taala uskey kaam bikher deta hai aur uska faqr uski aakhon key samney kar deta hai aur usey duniya itni hi milti hai jitni uskey liye muqaddar hai aur jiski niyat aakhirat ka husool ho, Allah Taala uskey kaam murtab kar deta hai aur uskey dil mein istighnaa paida farma deta hai aur duniya zaleel ho kar uskey paas aati hai."
4106,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap farma rahey they : jo shakhs sarey taffakuraat ko jama kar key eik hi fikr, yani aakhirat ki fikr mein dhaal ley, Allah us ko duniyaawi taffakuraat sey beniyaz kar deta hai. aur jisey duniya key maamlat key taffakuraat mukhtalif ghaatiyon mein liye phiren, Allah ko uski parwah nahin hoti ke wo (un taffakuraat ki) kon si wadi mein halak hota hai."
4107,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marfooan marvi hai ke Allah Subhaanhu w Taala farmata hai : Adam key betey ! meri ibadat key liye farigh ho ja , main tera Sina istighnaa (beniyaazi) sey bhar dunga aur tera faqr (ghareebi) door kar dunga. aur agar tu ney aisa na kiya to main terey seeney ko ishghal sey bhar dunga aur tera faqr door nahin karunga."
4108,"Hazrat Mustaurid bin Shaddad bin Amr Qarshi Fahri (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap farma rahey they : aakhirat key muqabley mein duniya ki misal aisey hai jaisey koi shakhs samandar mein ungli daley, phir dekhey ke usney kitna pani ley liya hai."
4109,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chataai par (aaram karney key liye) letey to uskey nishan aap key jism Mubarak par zahir ho gaey. mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! agar aap hamein farmatey to hum aap key liye koi chiz (bistar waghera) bichha detey jis key sath is (chataai ki sakhti) sey bachao ho jata. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mera duniya sey kya talluq ! meri aur duniya ki misal to aisey hai, jaisey koi sawar (musafir) saye key liye darkht key nichey thehra, phir usey chhod kar rawana ho gaya."
4110,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Zul-Hulefa key maqam par they. achcha aap ko (raastey mein) eik miri hui bakri nazar aai, ( wo mar kar phool gaee thi aur) uski taang ooper uthi hui thi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara kya khayal hai, kya ye bakri Malik ki nazar mein haqeer hai? qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! jitni ye bakri Malik ki nazar mein haqeer hai, duniya Allah ki nazar mein is sey ziyada haqeer hai. agar duniya Allah key yahan eik machchhar key par key barabar bhi wazan rakhti to wo kisi kafir ko kabhi eik qatra bhi peeney ko na deta."
4111,"Hazrat Mustaurid bin Shaddad Qarshi (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main eik qafley mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha ke aap ka guzar eik phenkey huye (murda) memney key paas sey huwa. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tumharey khayal mein ye memnaa malikon ki nazar mein be-qadr hai? unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! unhoney be-qadr samajh kar hi phenka hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! jitna ye memnaa malikon ki nazar mein haqeer hai, Allah key yahan duniya is sey bhi ziyada haqeer hai."
4112,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : duniya maloon hai. is mein jo kuch hai, sab maloon hai, siwaye Allah key zikr key aur us sey talluq rakhney wali ashiya (cheezon) key, aur siwaye Aalim aur Talibe-ilm key."
4113,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : duniya momin ka qaid khana aur kafir ki jannat hai."
4114,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney merey jism ka eik hissa (kandhaa) pakad kar farmaya : Abdullah ! duniya mein aisey reh, goya to pardesi hai, goya to musafir hai. aur apney aap ko qabron walon (murdon) mein shumar kar."
4115,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya main tujhey jannat key badshah na bataun? (har) zaeef aadmi, kamzor samjha janey wala (log usey kamzor samjhen aur us sey kisi qisam ka koi khatra mehsus na keren) do puraney kapdon mein libaas mein. (lekin Allah key yahan itna buland maqam hai ke) agar Allah key naam sey qism kha ley to wo uski qism puri kar deta hai."
4116,"Hazrat Harisa bin Wahab Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya main tumhen jannat waley na bataun? har zaeef aadmi, kamzor samjha janey wala (jannati hai).  kya main tumhen jahannam waley na bataun? har durusht khoo, zarparast, mutakabbir hai."
4117,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey nazdik sab sey ziyada qabile-rashk wo momin hai jo halka-phulkaa (kam aamdani wala) ho, usey namaz sey bahut ziyaada hissa mila ho (nafli namaz aur tahajjud ziyada padhta ho). logon mein gumnaam ho, uski parwah na ki jati ho, usey zarurat key mutabiq rizq muyassar ho (itna ziyada rizq na ho ke bacha kar rakha jaaey), wo is par sabr karey (mazeed ka lalach na kerey), usey jaldi maut aa jaey, uska tarka thoda ho, aur usey roney waliyan bhi kam hon."
4118,"Hazrat Abu-Umama Haarisi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : saadgi eman mein sey hai. Raavi ney kaha : saadgi sey murad maamuli libas aur ghiza par iktifa karna hai."
4119,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazeed (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farma rahey they. kya main tumhen tumharey behtareen afrad ki nishan dahi na karun? Sahaba ney arz kiya : kyon nahin Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : tumharey behtareen afrad wo hain jin ko dekh kar Allah ki yad aaye."
4120,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey eik aadmi guzraa. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum us shakhs key barey mein kya kehtey ho? unhoney arz kiya : uskey barey mein aap ki raey ziyada sahih hai. hum to (apni maloomat key mutabiq) ye kehtey hain : ye shakhs moazziz (dolat mand) afrad mein sey hai. uskey barey mein yehi tawaqqo hai ke agar (kisi gharaney mein) nikah ka pegham dey to uska pegham qubul kiya jaaey, agar ( kisi ki) sifarish karey to uski sifarish qubul ki jaaey, aur agar baat karey to uski baat suni jaey (aur usey ahmiyat di jaey). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh ho gaey. (phir) eik aur aadmi guzra to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is shakhs key barey main tum kya kehtey ho? unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! qism hai Allah ki ! hum to kehtey hain ke ye eik gharib musalman hai. uskey barey mein tawaqqo hai ke agar nikah ka pegham dey to usey rishta na diya jaey. agar sifarish karey to uski sifarish qubul na ki jaey. agar baat karey to uski baat na suni jaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye (gharib musalman) us (pehley) shakhs jaisey zamin bhar aadmiyon sey behtar hai."
4121,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala apney momin, tang dast , sawal sey bachney waley , baal bachchon waley bandey sey mohabbat farmata hai."
4122,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Nadaar (ghareeb) momin dolat mandon sey aadha din, yani paanch-sau saal pehley jannat mein jaeyngey."
4123,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nadaar (ghareeb) muhajrin ghani muhaajiron sey paanch-sau saal pehley jannat mein dakhil hongey."
4124,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : nadaar (ghareeb) muhajrin ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey shikayat ki ke Allah Taala ney ehale-sarwat (daulat-mand) hazraat ko un par fazilat ata farmaai hai (jis ki wajeh sey wo log maali nekiyan ziyada kar key buland darjaat hasil kar saktey hain). aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey naadaaron (ghareebon) ki jamaat ! kya main tumhen khush khabri na dun? nadaar (ghareeb) momin dolat-mand mominon sey aadha din, yani paanch-sau saal pehley jannat mein dakhil hongey. phir (ye hadees suna kar hadees key eik Raavi) Hazrat Musa (bin Ubeda (Rahimahullah)) ney ye aayat tilawat ki : (وَ اِنَّ یَومًا عِنْدَ رَبِّکَ کَاَلْفِ سَنَةٍ مِّمَّا تَعُدُّوْنَ),''aap key Rab key nazdik eik din tumhari ginti key aetbar sey eik hazar saal ka hai.''"
4125,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Jaafar bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) gharibon sey mohabbat kartey aur unkey paas beth kar un sey baaten kartey aur un ki baaten suntey they. aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un (Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu)) ko Abul-masakin ki kunniyat sey yad farmaya kartey they."
4126,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : miskinon sey mohabbat kiya karo kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko in alfaz key sath dua kartey suna hai : (اَللّٰھُمَّ اَحْیِنِی مِسْکِیْنًا , اَمِتْنِی مِسْکِیْنًا o احْشُرْنِی فِی زُمْرَۃِ الْمَسَاکِیْن), ''aey Allah ! mujhey miskeen bana kar zinda rakh aur miskeen bana kar faut kar aur mujhey miskinon ki jamaat mein utha.''"
4127,"Hazrat Abu Kanood (Abdullah bin Aamir) Azdi (Rahimahullah) ney Hazrat Khubab sey riwayat kartey huye is aayate-mubaarka ki tafseer mein ye hadees bayan farmaai : irshaade Bari Taala hai : (وَلَا تَطْرُدِ الَّذِينَ يَدْعُونَ رَبَّهُم بِالْغَدَاةِ وَالْعَشِيِّ يُرِيدُونَ وَجْهَهُ padhi. ما عَلَيْكَ مِنْ حِسَابِهِم مِّن شَيْءٍ وَمَا مِنْ حِسَابِكَ عَلَيْهِم مِّن شَيْءٍ فَتَطْرُدَهُمْ فَتَكُونَ مِنَ الظَّالِمِينَ), ''aur un logon ko apney sey door mat karen jo apney parwardigar ko subah aur Sham pukartey (aur uski ibadat kartey) hain. wo apney apney Rab ka chehra (raza-mandi) chahtey hain. unkey hisab mein sey kisi chiz ka bojh aap par nahin, aur aap key hisab mein sey kisi chiz ka bojh un par nahin, phir agar aap in ko apney sey door kerengey to aap zalimon mein sey ho jaaeyngey. (Hazrat Khubab (Raziallahu anhu) ney) farmaya : (Islam qubul karne sey pehley) Hazrat Aqra bin Habis Tameemi aur Hazrat Uena bin Mohsin Fazari (Raziallahu anhuma) aaye to dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kamzor (nadaar) musalmanon ki jamaat mein Hazrat Suheb, Hazrat Bilaal, Hazrat Ammar aur Hazrat Khubab Raziallahu anhum aur aisey hi kuchh doosrey gharib aur kamzor mominon key sath tashrif farma hain. jab unhoney un hazraat ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ird-gird bethey dekha to unhen haqeer jaana. unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey tanhai mein baat ki aur kaha : hum chahtey hain ke aap hamarey sath (alag sey) tashrif rakhen taake ehale-Arab ko hamari fazilat (aur buland maqam) ka pata chaley kyonkey aap key paas Arab (key mukhtalif ilaqon) key wafad aatey hain, aur hamein is baat sey sharam mehsus hoti hai ke Arab key log hamein in ghulamon key sath bethey huye dekhen, isliye jab hum aap key paas aaya karen to aap unhen apney paas sey utha diya keren, jab hum farigh ho jaeyn to phir aap chahen to unkey sath bhi tashrif rakhen. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : theek hai. unhoney kaha : hamein (is muahidey ki) eik tehreer likh dijiye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney likhney ka saman talab farmaya, aur likhney key liye Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula liya. hum (gharib musalman) eik taraf bethey they. itney mein Jibril (Alaihissalam) utrey aur ('wahi' ki aayaat sunatey huye) farmaya : (وَلَا تَطْرُدِ الَّذِينَ . . الظَّالِمِينَ) phir Aqra bin Habis aur Uena bin Hisn (Raziallahu anhuma) ka zikr kiya (jo us waqt ghair Muslim they) aur farmaya : (وَكَذَٰلِكَ فَتَنَّا بَعْضَهُم بِبَعْضٍ لِّيَقُولُوا أَهَـٰؤُلَاءِ مَنَّ اللَّـهُ عَلَيْهِم مِّن بَيْنِنَا padhi. أَلَيْسَ اللَّـهُ بِأَعْلَمَ بِالشَّاكِرِينَ),aur isi tarah hamney baaz ko baaz key zariey sey aazmaaish mein dala hai taake wo log (unhen dekh kar) kahin : kya hum mein sey ye log hain jin par Allah ney ehsan kiya hai? kya Allah apney shukar guzar bandon ko (un sey) ziyada nahin janta? phir farmaya : ( وَإِذَا جَاءَكَ الَّذِينَ . . . الرَّحْمَةَ ),aur jab aap key paas wo log aayen jo hamari aayaton par eman rakhtey hain to keh dijiye tum par salam ho. tumharey Rab ney meharbani ko apney zimmey lazim kar liya hai. Hazrat Khubab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : chunanche hum log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key qarib aagey yahan tak key hamney aap key ghutnon sey apney ghutney mila diye. phir (ye keyfiyat ho gaee ke) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey sath (kafi der tak) bethey rehtey. phir jab aap uthna chahtey to tashrif ley jaatey aur hamein bethey rehney detey. tab Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farmaai : (وَاصْبِرْ نَفْسَكَ . فُرُطًا),aur apney aap ko un logon key sath rokey rakhiye jo subah Sham apney Rab ko pukartey hain.wo uski raza key Talib hain. aap ki nazren unhen chhod kar doosrey logon ki taraf na jaeyn (un sardaron key sath na bethein) ke aap duniya ki zindagi ki zeenat chaahne lagen. aur aap us shakhs ki baat na maanen jis key dil ko hamney apni yad sey ghafil kar diya hai. (Uena aur Aqra waghera ki) aur jo apni khahish key peechhey chalta hai, aur uska maamla had aetidaal (beech ke raaste) sey hata huwa hai (halakat ka baais hai) Sahaba bayan kartey hain : is sey murad Uena aur Aqra ka maamla hai. phir Allah Taala ney do aadmiyon ka waqiyaa bayan farmaya aur duniya ki zindagi ki misal bayan farmaai. Hazrat Khubab (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : (uskey baad) hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath bethtey they lekin jab wo waqt aata jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key uthney ka (roz marra ka) hota tha to hum khud hi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko chhod kar uth jatey they taake aap bhi tashrif ley ja saken."
4128,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : ye aayat hum chhe afrad key barey mein nazil hui hai : merey barey mein. hazraat Abdullah bin Masood, Suheb, Ammar, Miqdaad aur Bilal Raziallahu anhum key barey mein. unhoney farmaya : Quraish ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha : hum in (gharib afrad) sey kam tar nahin ban'na chahtey, lihaza unhein apney paas sey hata dijiye. is baat sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key dil mein Allah ki mashiyat sey koi khayal aaya to Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farma di : ( وَلَا تَطْرُدِ الَّذِينَ يَدْعُونَ رَبَّهُم بِالْغَدَاةِ وَالْعَشِيِّ يُرِيدُونَ وَجْهَهُ padhi. ),''un logon ko apney paas sey mat hataaiye jo subh aur Sham apney Rab ko uski raza key husool key liye pukartey hain.''"
4129,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ziyada maal rakhney walon key liye halakat hai magar jisney maal ko is tarah, is tarah, is tarah aur is tarah (kharch) kiya. ye farmatey huye Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney daain, baain, aagey aur peechhey chaaron taraf (har taraf eik baar) ishara farmaya."
4130,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ziyada maal waley qiyamat key din (doosron sey darjaat mein) nichey hongey, magar jisney maal ko is tarah aur is tarah kharch kiya, aur uski kamai paak (aur halal zaraey) sey hui."
4131,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ziyada maal waley ziyada nichey hongey , magar jisney is tarah , is tarah aur is tarah kharch kiya. (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney) teen baar (ishara) farmaya."
4132,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar merey paas uhad pahad jitna sona ho to main nahin chahunga ke mujh par teesri raat aaye aur (us waqt bhi) is mein sey kuchh merey paas (bacha huwa) mojud ho, magar itni chiz jisey mein qarz ki adaaegi key liye sanbhaal rakhun."
4133,"Hazrat Amr bin Ghelaan Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ya Allah ! jo shakhs mujh par eman laya, meri tasdeeq ki aur usney (dil sey) jaan liya ke main jo (shariyat) ley kar aaya hun wo teri taraf sey haq hai, to usey kam maal aur aulad dey , aur usey apni mulaqat ki mohabbat nasib farma aur usey jaldi maut ata farma. aur jo mujh par eman na laya, meri tasdeeq na ki aur ye yaqin na kiya ke main jo (shariyat) ley kar aaya hun wo teri taraf sey haq hai, us ko bahut maal aur aulad dey, aur uski umr taweel (lambi) farma dey."
4134,"Hazrat Naqaadah (bin Abdullah) Asadi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey eik aadmi ki taraf bhej kar us sey eik oontni talab farmaai. us shakhs ney (oontni deney sey) inkar kar diya. phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey eik aur aadmi ki taraf bheja. usney eik oontni bhijwa di. jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney oontni ko dekha to farmaya : ya Allah ! is mein barkat ata farma aur isey bhejney waley ko bhi. Hazrat Naqaadah (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey kaha jo usey ley kar aaya (uskey liye bhi barkat ki dua farmaaeyn). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aur jo usey ley kar aaya ( Allah usey bhi barkat dey). phir aap key hukm sey usey dohaa gaya, usney bahut doodh diya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us pehley shakhs key barey mein, jisney inkar kar diya tha, farmaya : ya Allah ! falan ka maal ziyada farma. aur jisney oontni bheji thi uskey haq mein farmaya : ya Allah ! us ko roz ka rizq roz dey."
4135,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : halak ho jaey (tabah ho jaey) Dinar ka banda, Dirham ka banda, kambal ka banda aur chadar ka banda. agar usey diya jaey to khush rehta hai, agar na diya jaey to (baiat wala) wada pura nahin karta."
4136,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : halak ho jaey Dinar ka banda, Dirham ka banda, aur chadar ka banda, halak ho jaaey, ondha ho jaey, usey kaanta lagey to nikala na jaey."
4137,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ameeri saman ki kasrat sey nahin hoti balke ameeri to dil ki ameeri hai."
4138,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kamiyab wo hai jisey Islam ki hidayat mil gaee, zarurat key mutabiq rizq mil gaya aur wo is par qinaat karne wala ho gaya."
4139,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ya Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ghar walon ko zaruri haajaat key mutabiq rizq ata farma."
4140,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din har dolat-mand aur nadaar (ghareeb) ki khahish yehi hogi ke usey duniya mein sirf (zinda rakhney key qabil) thodi si rozi mili hoti."
4141,"Hazrat Ubedullah bin Mohsin Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jiski subah is haal mein hui ke usey badan mein aafiyat, apney barey mein aman aur din bhar ki khurak hasil ho, usey goya puri duniya jama kar key dey di gaee."
4142,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (duniya mein) apney sey nichey waley (kam maal) ko dekho, apney sey ooper waley ko na dekho, us sey ye hoga ke tum Allah ki nemat ko haqeer na samjho gey. (hadees ke raawi) Abu-Muaawia ney (Namllah) key baad (Alaikum) key alfaz bhi bayan kiye hain."
4143,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala tumhari Suraton aur maalon ko nahin dekhta balke tumharey amalon aur dilon ko dekhta hai."
4144,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum, aale Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mahina mahina is haal mein guzar detey they ke aag nahin jalaatey they. (hamara khana) sirf khajuren aur pani hota tha."
4145,"Uummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ghar walon par mahina bhar is tarah guzar jata tha ke aap key kisi ghar mein bhi dhuwan nazar nahin aata tha. (Hazrat Abu-Salma (Rahimahullah) ney bayan kiya : ) mainey kaha : phir wo log kya khatey they? Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : do siyah cheezen : khajuren aur pani, albatta hamarey kuchh Ansari hamsaaey they, wo mukhlis hamsaaey they, unkey gharon mein palne-waali kuchh bakriyan thin (jinhen charney key liye charaagaah mein nahin ley jaya jata tha, ghar la kar chaara diya jata tha). wo unka doodh aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf (hamarey yahan) bhej diya kartey they. (Raavi hadees) Muhammad bin Amr (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : wo no ghar they."
4146,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bhook ki wajeh sey karwaten badaltey dekha kyonkey aap ko maamuli si khajuren bhi muyassar na thin jin sey pet bhar letey."
4147,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kaee baar ye farmatey suna hai : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ki jaan hai ! aaj Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) key ghar walon key paas eik saa ghalla hai na eik saa khajuren. un dino Rasool Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki nau biwiyan thin."
4148,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aaj Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (key ghar walon key paas sirf eik mud khurak hai. ya farmaya : eik mud khurak bhi nahin hai."
4149,"Hazrat Salman bin Surd (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye to (hamari ye haalat thi ke) hamein teen raat tak khana muyassar na ho saka."
4150,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein garm khana hazir kiya gaya. aap ney khaya. jab farigh huye to farmaya : Allah ka shukar hai merey pet mein itney din sey (taza aur) garm khana nahin gaya (khajoor waghera par guzaara raha)."
4151,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka bistar chamdey ka tha jis mein khajoor ki chhaal bhari hui thi."
4152,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Ali aur Fatima (Raziallahu anha) key yahan tashrif ley gaey. us waqt un dono ney eik safed ooni chadar ley rakhi thi jo un dono ko Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney inayat farmaai thi, isi ke sath eik izkhir ki ghaas bhara gaddaa diya tha aur eik mishkeeza."
4153,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key yahan hazir huwa to aap eik chataai par tashrif farma they. main beth gaya, mainey dekha ke aap ney sirf teh-band pehan rakha hai, doosra koi kapda zebe-tan nahin. mainey dekha ke aap key pehlu par chataai sey nishan pad gaey hain. eik taraf sirf thodey sey jau they. ghaaliban eik saa hongey. aur keekar key pattey they (jo chamdey ki dabaaghat mein kaam aatey hain) aur baghair dabaaghat khaal latki hui thi. meri aakhon mein aansu aagaey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ibne Khittab ! aap kyon rotey hain? mainey kaha : Allah key Nabi ! main kyon na ro'un? is chataai sey aap key pehlu mein nishan pad gaey hain (koi naram bistar bhi nahin). aur aap key saman rakhney ki jagah mein kuchh nazar nahin aata, siwaye us (eik saa jau) key jo main dekh raha hun. udhar Kisraa aur Qaisar baaghon aur mewon mein (aesh kar rahey) hain. aap Allah key Nabi aur uskey barguzeeda (chuney huey) hain, aur ye aap ka tosha khana hai (jo khaali pada hai). Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Khittab key betey ! kya to is baat sey khush nahin ke hamein aakhirat mil jaey aur un (Qaisar aur Kisraa) ko duniya? mainey kaha : kyon nahin ! (main khush hun)"
4154,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki beti (Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha)) rukhsat ho kar merey ghar aayen, us raat hamara bistar sirf eik mendhey ki khaal par mushtamil tha."
4155,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Aqba bin Amr Ansari) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sadqey ka hukm detey to (hamari ye kaifiyat hoti thi ke) hum mein sey koi aadmi ja kar mazduri karta aur eik mudd (khajoor ya jo waghera) ley kar aata (aur usey sadqey key tor par pesh kar deta). aaj to eik aadmi key paas eik lakh ki raqam bhi mojud hai. (Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key shagrid) Hazrat Shaqeeq (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : ghaaliban unka ishara khud apni taraf tha."
4156,"Hazrat Khalid bin Umer (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hamein Hazrat Utba bin Ghazawaan (Raziallahu anhu) ney member par khutba diya aur (us mein ye bhi) farmaya : mainey dekha hai ke hum saat afrad Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. hamein khaney key liye darakhton key patton key siwa kuchh bhi muyassar na tha. (hum wohi khatey rahey) yahan tak key hamari baachhein zakhmi ho gaeen."
4157,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhen bhook ka samna karna pada jabke wo saat afrad they. wo farmatey hain : mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney saat khajuren inayat farmaeen. har aadmi key liye eik khajoor.
4158,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhuma) apney walid Hazrat Zuber bin Awam (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan kartey hain, unhoney kaha : jab ye aayat nazil hui : ( ثُمَّ لَتُسْأَلُنَّ يَوْمَئِذٍ عَنِ النَّعِيمِ ),''phir us din tum sey nematon key barey mein zarur sawal hoga."" Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : hum sey kon si nematon key barey mein sawal hoga? hamein to sirf pani aur khajuren hi muyassar hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aagah raho ! ye (sawal) zarur hoga."
4159,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (eik jihaadi muhim par) rawana farmaya. hum teen sau afrad they. hum apni ghizaai ashiya (cheeze) apni gardanon par uthaey huye they. (muhim key doran mein) hamari khurak khatam ho gaee yahan tak key eik eik aadmi key hissey main eik eik khajoor aati thi. kisi ney kaha : Abu-Adbullah ! eik khajoor sey aadmi ka kya guzaara hota hoga? unhoney farmaya : uska ehsas hamein us waqt huwa jab wo (eik eik khajoor) bhi na rahi. (aakhir) hum samandar par pahunchey to achcha eik badi machhli nazar aai jisey samandar ney (pani sey bahir) phenk diya tha. hum (sara lashkar) is mein sey atthaara din tak khatey rahey."
4160,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log apni eik jhaunpdi ki marammat kar rahey they ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas sey guzrey to aap ney farmaya : ye kya hai? mainey kaha : hamari jhaunpdi kamzor ho gaee hai, hum isey theek kar rahey hain. aap ney farmaya : merey khayal main to maamla us sey jald waqey honey wala hai."
4161,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik gol khemey key paas sey guzrey jo eik Ansari Sahaba key darwazey par bana huwa tha. aap ney farmaya : ye kya hai? logon ney kaha : gol khema hai jo falan ney banaya hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo maal bhi is tarah (bila zarurat kharch) ho, wo qiyamat key din apney Malik key liye wabal ka baais hoga. Ansari ko Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key us farman ka ilm huwa to usney wo khema hata diya. baad mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wahan sey guzrey to wo khema nazar na aaya. aap ney uskey barey mein puchha to bataya gaya ke Ansari ko aap key farman ka ilm huwa to usney isey hata diya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah is par rehmat farmaaey. Allah is par rehmat farmaaey."
4162,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath hota tha (aur aap hayaat they) to mainey ye kaifiyat bhi dekhi ke mainey eik kamra banaya jo mujhey barish sey mehfooz rakh sakey aur dhoop sey bacha sakey. uski taamir mein meri kisi shakhs ney madad na ki."
4163,"Hazrat Harisa bin muzrib (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hum log Hazrat Khubab (Raziallahu anhu) ki bimar pursi key liye unkey yahan hazir huye to unhoney farmaya : meri bimari lambi ho gaee hai. agar mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye farman : maut ki tamanna na karo. na suna hota to main zarur maut ki dua karta. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye bhi farmaya : bandey ko apney tamam (jayez) ikhrajaat karney ka sawab milta hai magar jo mitti mein kharch kiya jaey. ya farmaya : imarat bananey mein kharch kiya jaey (uska sawab nahin milta)."
4164,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : agar tum log Allah par is tarah bharosa karo jaisey is par bharosa karney ka haq hai to wo tumhen is tarah rizq dey jaisey parindon ko rizq deta hai. wo subah (ghaunslon sey) bhookey rawana hotey hain aur Sham ko sair ho kar aatey hain."
4165,"Hazrat Hiba bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Siwa bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Khidmat mein hazir huye to aap kisi chiz ki marammat kar rahey they. hamney us kaam mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki madad ki. aap ney farmaya : jab tak tumharey sar harkat kartey rahen, rizq sey na ummid mat hona. insan ko uski maa janti hai to wo (gosht key lothdey ki tarah) surkh hota hai jis par mazbut khaal bhi nahin hoti phir bhi Allah usey rizq mohaiyya farmata hai."
4166,"Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : insan key dil ki eik eik shaakh har wadi mein hoti hai (wo dunyawi mafad key liye har raastey par chalney key liye tayyar hota hai). jis shakhs ka dil har wadi key peechhey pad jata hai (duniya key liye har mashghooliyat mein giraftar ho jata hai), Allah ko uski parwah nahin hoti ke usey kis wadi mein tabah kar dey. aur jo Allah par tawakkul karta hai (Allah ki taraf tawajjoh rakhtey huye yaqin karta hai ke jayez rizq uskey liye kafi hoga), usey Allah Taala intishaar sey bacha leta hai (aur wo itminan ki zindagi guzaarta hai)."
4167,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har shakhs ko is haal mein maut aani chahiye ke wo Allah key barey mein achchha guman rakhta ho."
4168,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kamzor momin ki nisbat taqatwar momin behtar hai aur Allah ko ziyada pyara hai. aur sab mein khair mojud hai. jo chiz tujhey nafa dey sakti hai, uski (koshish aur) hirs kar aur aajiz na ban. agar tujh par (teri marzi key khilaf) koi chiz ghalib aa jaey to keh : ye Allah ka faisla hai. usney jo chaha kiya. (lafz لَوْ ) yaani 'agar' sey bach kyonkey 'agar' sey shetan ka kaam shuru ho jata hai."
4169,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aqalmandi ki baat momin ki gum-shuda chiz hai. wo usey jahan miley , usey leney ka ziyada haq rakhta hai."
4170,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : do nematen aisi hain jinkey barey mein aksar log khasarey ka shikar hain : sehat aur faraaghat."
4171,"Hazrat Abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey (deen ki baaten) sikhlaaey aur ikhtisaar kijiye : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to namaz padhney khada ho to aisey namaz padh jaisey to duniya sey rukhsat honey wala ho. aur koi aisi baat na keh jis sey (baad mein) mazrat kerni padey. aur logon key haath mein jo kuchh hai us sey puri tarah mayus ho ja."
4172,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs hikmat ki baat sunta hai, phir apney (sunaney waley) sathi ki wo baat (doosron ko) sunata hai jo sab sey buri ho. (maslan : khateeb ney khutbey mein jo achchhi baaten bayan ki hain, wo dusron ko nahin batata, sirf ye bayan karta hai ke aaj khateeb ney falan baat aisi kahi jo ghalat hai), uski misal aisey hai, jaisey eik aadmi eik charwahey key paas gaya, aur kaha : charwahey ! apney rewad mein sey mujhey eik gosht wali bakri dey dey (jisey zibeh kar key main gosht kha sakoon). charwahey ney kaha : ja kar rewad ki behtareen (bakri) ka kaan pakad ley (aur ley ja). wo saail gaya aur rewad key kuttey ka kaan pakad liya. (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key shagrid) Abul-Hasan Qataan (Rahimahullah) ney yehi riwayat Ismaeel bin Ibrahim key wastey sey usi key hum maana bayan ki aur is mein kaha : is rewad ki behtareen bakri ka kaan (pakad ley)."
4173,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis key dil mein raai key eik daney jitna bhi takabbur hoga, wo jannat mein nahin jaeyga. aur jis key dil mein raai key eik daney jitna bhi eman hoga, wo jahannam mein nahin jaeyga."
4174,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah farmata hai : badaai meri chadar hai aur azmat mera pehnaawa hai. jo shakhs in mein sey koi chiz bhi mujh sey kheencheyga, main usey jahannam mein phenk dunga."
4175,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Paak farmata hai : badaai meri chadar hai aur azmat mera pehnaawa hai. jo shakhs in mein sey koi chiz bhi mujh sey kheencheyga, main usey aag mein phenk dunga."
4176,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Paak (ki khushnoodi) key liye eik darja tawaazeh ikhtiyar karta hai, Allah Taala uskey badley uska eik darja buland karta hai. aur jo shakhs Allah key samney eik darja takabbur ikhtiyar karta hai, Allah Taala uskey badley uska eik darja kam kar deta hai yahan tak key (darjaat kam hotey hotey ye nobat aa jati hai ke) usey sab sey nichley tabqey mein dal deta hai."
4177,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Madina walon ki eik londi bhi Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka haath pakad leti thi to aap uskey haath sey apna haath nahin chhudaatey they yahan tak key wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apney kisi kaam key liye Madina mein jis jagah chahti ley jaati."
4178,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bimar ki iyaadat farmatey, janaazey key sath jatey, ghulam ki dawat qubul kartey aur gadhey par sawar ho jaya kartey they. banu Qureza aur banu-Nazeer key din (jis din banu-Quraiza aur banu-Nazeer wala waqiyaa huwa) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik gadhey par sawar they. aur jange-khaibar key moqey par aap eik gadhey par sawar they jiski lagaam khajoor key patton sey bani hui rassi ki thi. aur aap key nichey khajoor key patton ki zeen thi."
4179,"Hazrat Ayaaz bin Himaar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khutba irshad farmaya, is mein aap ney ye bhi farmaya : Allah ney mujh par ""wahi"" nazil ki hai ke tawaazeh (mehmaan-nawaazi) ikhtiyar karo yahan tak key koi kisi par fakhr na karey."
4180,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) parda nasheen kanwari ladki sey ziyada hayaadaar they. agar aap ko koi baat nagawar guzarti to chehra Mubarak par uskey aasaar zahir ho jatey they."
4181,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har Deen mein koi na koi imtiyaazi aur akhlaaqi khoobi hoti hai. Islam ki imtiyaazi khoobi hayaa hai."
4182,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har Deen ki koi na koi imtiyaazi aur akhlaaqi khoobi hoti hai. Islam ki imtiyaazi khoobi hayaa hai."
4183,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon tak pehli nabuwat ka jo kalam pahuncha hai, is mein ye bhi hai : jab to hayaa na karey to jo chahey kar."
4184,"Hazrat abu-Bakra ( Nufey bin Haris Saqafi) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hayaa eman ka hissa hai aur eman jannat mein (ley janey wala) hai. aur badkalaami badakhlaaqi ka hissa hai aur badakhlaaqi jahannam mein (ley janey wali) hai."
4185,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : be hayai jis chiz mein bhi ho, usey badmazaa kar deti hai. aur hayaa jis chiz mein bhi ho, usey khushnuma kar deti hai."
4186,"Hazrat Muaz bin Anas Juhni Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney apna ghussa rok liya jabke wo ghussey (key mutabiq sakhti) nafiz (laagu) karney ki taqat rakhta tha, usey qiyamat key din Allah Taala sab makhluqat key samney bula kar ikhtiyar dega ke jaun si hoor chahey pasand kar ley."
4187,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas bethey huye they ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey paas qabila Abdul-Qais ka wafad aa gaya hai. us waqt hum mein sey kisi ka ye khayal nahin tha (ke wo pahunch gaey hain). achcha wo log aaye aur sawaariyon sey utar kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho gaey. (un key sardar) Hazrat Ashja' (Malik bin Munzir) Asaree (Raziallahu anhu) baqi reh gaey. wo baad mein hazir huye. wo qiyam-gaah par utrey, sawari ko bithaya, apney (safar key) kapdey eik taraf rakhey (safar key kapdey utaar kar doosrey pehney), phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen farmaya : Ashja' ! tumharey andar do aisi aadatein hain jo Allah ko pasand hain : burdbaari sey aur sahaj mein kaam karna. unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kya ye chiz merey andar fitri tor par mojud hai ya baad mein paida hui? Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : balke ye chiz tumharey andar fitri tor par mojud hai."
4188,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Ashaj Asaree (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : tumharey andar do khubiyan hain jo Allah ko pasand hain. hilm (burdbaari) aur hayaa."
4189,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghussey ka wo ghoont jisey koi banda Allah ki raza key liye pi leta hai, Allah key yahan us sey badey sawab wala koi ghoont nahin."
4190,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main wo kuch dekhta hun jo tumhen nazar nahin aata, aur main wo kuchh sunta hun jo tumhen sunai nahin deta. aasman charcharaataa hai aur uska haq hai ke charcharaaey. is mein chaar ungliyon ki jagah bhi khaali nahin magar (balke har jagah) koi na koi farishta apni peshani rakhey huye Allah ko sajda kar raha hai. qism hai Allah ki ! agar tumhen wo kuchh malum ho jaey jo mujhey malum hai to tum thoda hanso aur ziyada ro'oo aur bistaron par aurton sey lutf andoz na ho sako aur tum ba-aawaze buland Allah sey fariyad kartey huye maidaanon mein nikal jao. qism hai Allah ki ! mera ji chahta hai (kash !)  main eik darkht hota jisey kaat diya jata ."
4191,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar tumhen wo kuchh malum ho jaey jo mujhey malum hai to tum hanso kam aur ro'oo ziyada."
4192,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : unkey Islam qubul karney key sirf chaar saal baad ye aayat nazil ho gaee thi jis mein Allah Taala ney unhen tanbih farmaai. (irshad hai)  (وَلَا يَكُونُوا كَالَّذِينَ أُوتُوا الْكِتَابَ مِن قَبْلُ فَطَالَ عَلَيْهِمُ الْأَمَدُ فَقَسَتْ قُلُوبُهُمْ padhi. وَكَثِيرٌ مِّنْهُمْ فَاسِقُونَ),''aur (ehael-emaan) un logon ki tarah na ho jaeyn jinhen pehley kitab di gaee thi, phir un par eik taweel (lambi) muddat guzri to unkey dil sakht ho gaey aur un mein sey aksar log nafarman hain.''"
4193,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ziyada mat hanso kyonkey ziyada hansney sey dil murda ho jata hai."
4194,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : mujhey Quran padh kar sunao. mainey Sura-Nisaa tilawat ki, jab main us aayat par pahuncha (فَكَيْفَ إِذَا جِئْنَا مِن كُلِّ أُمَّةٍ بِشَهِيدٍ وَجِئْنَا بِكَ عَلَىٰ هَـٰؤُلَاءِ شَهِيدًا),''us waqt kya haal hoga jab hum har ummat mein sey eik gawah hazir kerengey aur aap ko is ummat par gawah bana kar ley aayengey."" (Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain) mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf dekha to aap ki aakhon sey aansu beh rahey they."
4195,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum eik janaazey mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik qabr key kinarey par beth gaey aur itna roey ke mitti tar ho gaee. phir farmaya : bhaaiyo ! aisi chiz (qabr) key liye tayyari kar lo."
4196,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : roya karo. agar ronaa na aaye to roney ki si shakal bana lo (taake aansu aa jaeyn)."
4197,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis momin ki aakhon sey Allah key khof ki wajeh sey aansu nikal aayen, agar-che makkhi key sar jitney hi hon, phir wo aansu uskey chehrey key zahiri hissey (rukhsaaron) par lag jaaeyn, Allah Taala usey jahannam par haram kar dega."
4198,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! (Allah ka farman hai : )  (وَالَّذِينَ يُؤْتُونَ ما آتَوا وَّقُلُوبُهُمْ وَجِلَةٌ),''wo log jo Allah ki raah mein jo dena hota hai detey hain aur unkey dil dar rahey hotey hain.'' kya us sey murad wo aadmi hai jo zina, chori, aur sharab noshi ka murtakib hai? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin aey Abu-Bakar ki beti ! ya farmaya : nahin aey Siddiq ki beti ! is sey murad wo aadmi hai jo roza rakhta hai, sadqa deta hai aur namaz padhta hai, aur usey dar rehta hai ke shayad (uska amal) qubul na ho."
4199,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : amaalon ki misal bartan ki si hai. agar is mein nichey ka (pani waghera) achchha hoga to ooper wala hissa bhi achchha hoga. agar nichey wala kharab hoga to ooper wala bhi kharab hoga."
4200,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab banda dusron key samney bhi namaz achchhi padhey aur chup kar (tanhai mein) bhi namaz achchhi padhey to Allah Taala farmata hai : ye waaqaee mera banda hai."
4201,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aetidaal ikhtiyar karo aur sidhey raho. tum mein sey kisi ko bhi uska amal najat nahin dega. haazirin ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kya aap ko bhi nahin? farmaya : mujhey bhi nahin, siwaye uskey ke Allah mujhey apni rehmat aur apney Fazal mein chhupa ley."
4202,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah farmata hai : main doosrey sharikon key muqabley mein, sharaakat sey sab sey ziyada be-niyaz hun. jisney (ba-zahir) merey liye amal kiya, is mein merey siwa kisi aur ko bhi shareek kar liya to main us sey la-talluq ho jata hun. aur wo (amal) usi key liye hota hai jis ko usney (mera) shareek banaya."
4203,"Sabab Rasool Hazrat Abu Saad bin Abu Fuzaala Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab qiyamat key din Allah Taala pehley aur pichhley tamam insanon ko jama kerega, aur wo din aisa hai jis mein koi shak nahin, tab eik aelan karney wala aelan kerega : jisney Allah key liye kiye huye amal mein (kisi ko) shareek kiya, wo us amal ka sawab ghairullah hi sey maangey kyonkey Allah Taala doosrey sharikon key muqabley mein sharaakat sey sab sey ziyada be-niyaz hai."
4204,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas (ghar sey) bahar tashrif laye jabke hum Masih Dajjaal ka zikr kar rahey they. aap ney farmaya : kya main tumhen aisi chiz na bataaun jo merey nazdik tumharey liye Masih Dajjaal sey bhi ziyada khatarnaak hai? hamney kaha kyon nahin (farmaiye). Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chupa huwa shirk. (wo ye hai) ke aadmi namaz padhney khada hota hai, jab usey malum hota hai ke koi usey dekh raha hai to apni namaz ko khoobsurat banata hai."
4205,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey apni ummat par sab sey ziyada khof Allah key sath shirk karney ka hai. main ye nahin kehta ke wo suraj, chaand ya kisi but ko poojey-gey lekin aisey amal karengey. jo ghair Allah (ko dikhaney) key liye hongey aur poshida khahish rakhengey."
4206,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs shohrat key liye neki karta hai, Allah Taala uski tashheer kerega. aur jo shakhs dikhlaao karta hai, Allah uski haqiqat zahir kar dega."
4207,"Hazrat Jundub (bin Abdullah bin Sufiyan) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo dikhlaao karega, Allah uski haqiqat zahir kar dega. aur jo shohrat key liye neki karta hai, Allah uski tashheer (mash'hoor) karega."
4208,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hasad (rashk) sirf do hi kamon mein jayez hai. eik wo shakhs jis ko Allah ney maal diya aur usey haq ki raah mein kharch karney par laga diya (us sey rashk karna chahiye). aur doosra wo shakhs jisey Allah ney (deen ki) samajh di, wo uskey mutabiq faisley karta hai. aur uski taalim deta hai."
4209,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Hasad (rashk) sirf do kamon mein jayez hai. eik us aadmi sey (rashk karna chahiye) jisey Allah ney Quran (ka ilm) diya, wo raat key oqaat mein bhi is par qaaim rehta hai. aur din key oqaat mein bhi. aur (doosra) wo aadmi jis ko Allah ney maal diya, wo raat key oqaat mein bhi usey (neki key kamon mein) kharch karta hai aur din key oqaat mein bhi (us par rashk karna chahiye)."
4210,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hasad nekiyon ko is tarah kha jata hai jis tarah aag lakdiyon ko kha jati hai. aur sadqa gunahon (ki aag) ko is tarah bujha deta hai jis tarah pani (duniya ki) aag ko bujha deta hai. namaz momin ka Noor hai, aur roza jahannam sey (bachaney wali) dhaal hai."
4211,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Nufey bin Haris Saqafi) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ziyadti aur qata' Rehmi sey badh kar koi gunah aisa nahin jiski saza Allah Taala duniya mein bhi jaldi dey deta hai jabke uskey sath uskey liye aakhirat ka azab bhi sanbhaal rakhta hai."
4212,"Ummul-momineen Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab sey jaldi sawab neki aur sila rehmi (rishte-daaron sey husne-suluk) ka milta hai. aur (isi tarah) sab sey jaldi saza ziyadti aur qata'-rehmi (rishte daaron sey bad-salooki) ki milti hai."
4213,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : insan key liye itni burai kafi hai ke wo apney musalman bhai ki tahqeer karey (ya usey haqeer janey)."
4214,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Aa'alaa ney mujh par wahi nazil ki hai ke tawaazem (inkisaar) ikhtiyar karo aur koi kisi par ziyadti na karey."
4215,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahaba Hazrat Atiya (bin Urwa) Sa'di (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : banda taqwe key (buland) maqam tak nahin pahunchta hattaa key harj wali chiz sey bachney key liye wo chiz bhi chhod dey jis mein harj nahin (lekin shak hai ke shayad mana ho)."
4216,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya gaya. kon sa Aadmi afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : har saaf dil wala, sachchi zaban wala. Sahaba ney arz kiya sachchi zaban wala to hum jantey hain, saaf dil wala kon hota hai? aap ney farmaya : parhezgar, pak baaz, jis (key dil) mein na koi gunah ho, na ziyadti, na keena, na hasad."
4217,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Abu-Hurera ! muttaqi ho ja, to sab logon sey ziyada ibadat guzar ho jaaeyga. qanaa'at-pasand bin ja to sab sey ziyada shukar guzar ho jaaeyga. logon key liye wohi kuchh pasand kar jo apney liye pasand karta hai. to momin bin jaaeyga. apney hamsaaey key saath ham-saayegi ka achchaa talluq rakh, to Muslim bin jaaeyga, aur hasnaa kam kar dey kyonkey ziyada hansi dil ko murda kar deti hai."
4218,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tadbeer jaisi koi aql mandi nahin, '(haram waghera sey) parhez jaisa koi taqwaa nahin, Husne-khulq jaisa koi hasab nahin."
4219,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hasab maal hai, aur sharf taqwaa hai."
4220,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey eik farman, aur Usman Raavi ney kaha : eik aayat, malum hai, agar sab log is par amal kar lein to unkey liye kafi ho jaey. Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kon si aayat? aap ney farmaya : (وَمَن يَتَّقِ اللَّـهَ يَجْعَل لَّهُ مَخْرَجًا),''jo koi Allah sey darey, Allah uskey liye (har mushkil sey) nikalney ki raah bana deta hai.''"
4221,"Hazrat Abu-Zuhair (Muaz bin Ribah) Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney nabaawa ya banaawa key maqam par hum sey khitab farmaya, ye maqam Taaif key qarib hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ho sakta hai tum jannatiyon aur jahannamiyon ko alag alag pehchan lo. hamney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kis alamat sey? farmaya : achchhi raaey key izhar sey, aur buri raaey key izhar sey. tum eik doosrey par Allah key gawah ho."
4222,"Hazrat Kulsoom (bin Alqama) Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat main eik aadmi ney hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! jab main neki karun to mujhey kaisey malum ho sakta hai ke mainey achchha kaam kiya hai. aur jab main gunah kar bethun to kaisey malum hoga ke mainey bura kaam kiya hai? Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab terey hamsaaey kahin : tu ney achchha kaam kiya hai to (yaqeen kar ley ke) tu ney achchha kaam hi kiya hai, aur jab wo kahin : tu ney bura kaam kiya hai to phir tu ney bura kaam hi kiya hai."
4223,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : mujhey kaisey malum hoga jab main neki karun ya burai karun (ke mainey neki ki hai ya burai ki hai)? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to suney ke terey hamsaaey kahin : tu ney achchha kaam kiya hai to tu ney achchha kaam hi kiya hai. aur jab to unhein suney ke wo kahin tu ney bura kaam kiya hai to tu ney bura kaam hi kiya hai."
4224,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jannati aadmi wo hai jis key kanon ko Allah logon ki achchhi raey sey bhar deta hai, aur wo sun raha hota hai (ke log meri tareef kar rahey hain). aur jahannami wo hai jis key kanon ko Allah logon ki buri raey sey bhar deta hai aur wo sun raha hota hai (ke log mujhey achchha nahin samajhtey)."
4225,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! eik aadmi Allah ki raza key liye (khulus key sath) nek amal karta hai, uski wajeh sey log us sey mohabbat kartey hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye momin ko jaldi mil janey wali khushkhabri hai."
4226,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main eik amal karta hun (mera irada usey zahir karney ka nahin hota lekin) logon ko uska pata chal jata hai to mujhey achchha lagta hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tujhey do sawab milengey : khufiya neki ka sawab, aur elaniya neki ka sawab."
4227,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney logon ko khutba detey huye farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai, aap farma rahey they : amal to niyaton hi sey hain. aur har shakhs ko wohi kuchh milega . jiski usney niyat ki, chunanche jiski hijrat Allah aur uskey Rasool ki taraf hai, uski hijrat (ajr aur sawab key lihaz sey bhi) Allah aur uskey Rasool ki taraf hai. aur jiski hijrat duniya hasil karney key liye ya kisi aurat sey nikah karney key liye hai, uski hijrat usi ki taraf hai jis key paas wo hijrat kar key aaya hai."
4228,"Hazrat Abu-Kabsha (Saeed bin Amr) Anmaari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is ummat ki misal chaar afrad ki si hai : eik aadmi ko Allah ney maal aur ilm sey nawaza . wo apney maal mein ilm key mutabiq amal karta hai, usey jayez maqam par kharch karta hai. eik (doosra) aadmi wo hai jisey Allah ney ilm diya aur maal nahin diya. wo kehta hai : agar merey paas bhi us shakhs ki tarah (maal) hota to main bhi us (maal) sey aisey amal anjam deta jaisey ye (nek maal daar) anjam deta hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sawab mein ye dono barabar hain. aur eik (teesra) aadmi wo hai jisey Allah ney maal diya aur usey ilm nahin diya, chunanche wo apney maal ko andha dhund kharch karta hai. (yani) najaaiz maqam par kharch karta hai. aur eik (chotha) aadmi wo hai jisey Allah ney na ilm diya na maal diya wo kehta hai : agar merey paas is (burey maal daar) shakhs ki tarah maal hota to main bhi is (maal) sey aisey kaam karta jaisey ye (bura maal daar) karta hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye dono  teesra aur chotha (gunah mein barabar hain). Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney yehi riwayat dusri do sanadon sey bhi ba-wasta Abu-Kabsha (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey is (mazkura hadees) key hum maana bayan ki hai."
4229,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon ko (qiyamat key din) un ki niyaton key mutabiq uthaya jaaeyga."
4230,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon ko un ki niyaton key mutabiq (qabron sey) uthaya jaaeyga."
4231,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik chakor shakal ka khat (line) khinchaa. aur eik khat (line) us chakor key darmiyan mein khinchaa. aur chakor khat key darmiyan mein jo khat tha, uskey pehlu mein chand chhotey chhotey khat aur khinchey. aur eik khat us chakor sey nikalta huwa khinchaa, phir farmaya : kya tumhein malum hai ye kya hai? Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah aur uskey Rasool ko ziyada malum hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye darmiyani khat (line) insan hai. ye uskey pehlu key khutoot (liney) haadisey hain jo har jagah sey aa kar usey nochtey hain. agar wo is haadisey sey bach jaey to wo usey pakad leta hai. aur ye chakor khat maut ka hai jisney usey gher rakha hai. aur ye khat (line) jo bahar nikal raha hai, uski umeeden (aur aarzuein) hain."
4232,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye ibne-Adam hai aur ye uski maut hai, guddi key qarib. phir aagey ko haath badha kar farmaya : aur wahan tak uski umeeden hain."
4233,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : boodhey ka dil do chizon ki mohabbat mein jawan hota hai : zindagi ki mohabbat mein aur maal ki kasrat ki mohabbat mein."
4234,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ibne-Adam boodha hota jata hai aur uski do cheezen jawan hoti jati hain : maal ki hirs aur umr ki hirs."
4235,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ibne-Adam key paas maal ki do waadiyaan bhari hui hon to wo chahta hai ke unkey sath teesri wadi bhi ho. aur insan ka dil sirf mitti sey bharta hai, albatta jo shakhs tauba karey, Allah uski tauba qubul farmata hai."
4236,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat ki umrein saath aur sattar saal key darmiyan hongi. is sey aagey badhney waley kam hongey."
4237,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qism hai us (Allah) ki jo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (duniya sey) ley gaya ! aap jab faut huye to aap ziyada namaz (tahajjud) beth kar ada farmatey they. aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key nazdik ziyada pasandida amal wo nek amal tha jis par banda hameshgi karey agar-che thoda ho."
4238,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : merey paas eik aurat (bethi) thi ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas ( ghar mein) tashrif laye to aap ney farmaya : ye khatoon kon hai? mainey kaha : falan saahiba hai, jo soti nahin. Ummul-mominin ney un ki namaze tahajjud ka zikr kiya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : thehro ! wohi chiz ikhtiyar karo jiski tumhein taqat ho. qism hai Allah ki ! Allah nahin uktaataa yahan tak ke tum khud uktaa jaao. Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Deen ka wo kaam ziyada pasand tha jis par wo amal karney wala hamesha karey."
4239,"Hazrat Hanzalaa (bin Rabee bin Saifi) Tameemi Usedi (Raziallahu anhu) ''kaatibe-wahi'' sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke hamney jannat aur jahannam ka zikr kiya. ( to dil ki ye keyfiyat hui)  goya hum ( jannat aur jahannam ko) aakhon sey dekh rahey hain. phir main uth kar biwi bachchon key paas (ghar) chala gaya . main unkey sath hansa khelaa. (Hanzala ney) kaha : phir mujhey wo kaifiyat yad aai jis mein hum (Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki majlis mein) they, chunanche main (ghabra kar) bahar nikla to meri mulaqat Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey ho gaee . mainey kaha : main munafiq ho gaya, main munafiq ho gaya . Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney ( tafsil sun kar) farmaya : ye kaifiyat to hamari bhi hai. Hazrat Hanzala (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar ye kaifiyat arz ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Hanzala ! agar tum (hamesha) usi keyfiyat mein raho jis main tum merey paas hotey ho to farishtey tumharey bistaron par, ya (farmaya) raaston main tum sey musaafa karen. (lekin) Hanzala ! waqt waqt ki baat hai."
4240,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : itney amal ka bojh uthao jitney ki tumhein taqat ho kyonkey behtareen amal wo hai jis par ziyada pabandi ki jaey agar-che thoda ho."
4241,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi key paas sey guzrey jo eik chattan par namaz padh raha tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka key eik hissey mein (kisi kaam sey) tashrif ley aaye. wahan kuchh der tashrif farma rahey , phir wapis tashrif ley gaey to dekha ke wo aadmi isi tarah namaz padh raha hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dono haath jama kar key (ishara kartey huye) teen baar farmaya. logo ! (ifraat aur tafrit sey bach kar) darmiyaanaa raasta ikhtiyar karo. phir farmaya : Allah Taala (sawab deney sey) nahin uktaataa, tum hi (amal karney sey) uktaa jatey ho."
4242,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney arz kiya, Allah key Rasool ! kya hum sey un aamaal ka bhi muwaakhiza (poochh-gachh) hoga jo hum jahiliyat mein kartey they? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Islam la kar nek kaam kiye us sey jahiliyat mein honey waley aamaal ka muwaakhiza (poochh-gachh) nahin hoga. aur jisney (Islam la kar bhi) burey kaam kiye is sey pehley aur baad waley (sab aamal) ka muwaakhiza (poochh-gachh) hoga."
4243,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : aey Aaisha ! maamuli samjhey janey waley gunahon sey bachna , Allah key yahan unka bhi muwaakhiza (poochh-gachh) hoga."
4244,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab momin koi gunah karta hai to uskey dil par eik siyah nuqta lag jata hai. agar wo tauba kar ley , baaz aa jaey aur (Allah sey) bakhshish ki darkhaast karey to uska dil saaf ho jata hai. agar mazeed gunah karey to siyahi ka nuqta ziyada ho jata hai (yahan tak key hotey hotey dil bilkul siyah ho jata hai). yehi wo zang hai jis ka zikr Allah Taala ney apni kitab mein (is farman mein) kiya hai : (كَلَّا padhi. بَلْ padhi. رَانَ عَلَىٰ قُلُوبِهِم مَّا كَانُوا يَكْسِبُونَ),''yun nahin balke unkey dilon par unkey aamal ki wajeh sey zang chadh gaya hai.''"
4245,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main apni ummat key un afrad ko zarur pehchan lunga jo qiyamat key din tahaama key pahadon jaisi safed (roshan) nekiyan ley kar hazir hongey to Allah un (nekiyon ko) bikhrey huye ghubar mein tabdeel kar dega. Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! un ki sifaat bayan farma dijiye. un (ki kharaabiyon) ko hamarey liye waazeh kar dijiye. aisa na ho ke hum un mein shamil ho jaaeyn aur hamein pata bhi na chaley. aap ney farmaya : wo tumharey bhai hain aur tumhaari jins sey hain, aur raat ki ibadat ka hissa hasil kartey hain jis tarah tum kartey ho. lekin wo aisey log hain ke unhein jab tanhai mein Allah key haram karda gunahon ka moqey milta hai to unka irtikab kar letey hain."
4246,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya gaya kon sa amal sab sey ziyada ( logon ko) jannat mein dakhil kerega ? aap ney farmaya : taqwa aur khush-akhlaaqi. sawal kiya gaya : kon si chiz sab sey ziyada ( logon ko) jahannam mein ley jaeygi ? farmaya : do khokhli cheezen : munh aur sharmgah."
4247,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala tumhari tauba sey us sey ziyada khush hota hai jitna koi apni gum-shuda sawari paa kar khush hota hai."
4248,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar tum itni ghaltiyaan karo ke tumhaari ghaltiyaan aasman tak pahunch jaaeyn, phir tauba karo to (phir bhi) Allah tumhaari tauba qubul farmaeyga."
4249,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala apney bandey ki tauba ki wajeh sey us aadmi sey bhi ziyada khush hota hai jo kisi chatiyal sehra main apni sawari gum kar betha. usney isey talash kiya yahan tak key jab thak gaya to kapda odh kar let gaya. wo usi haal mein (letaa huwa) tha ke achcha usey apni sawari key paaon ki aawaz wahin sunai di jahan sey wo gum hui thi. usney chehrey sey kapda hataayaa to sawari sach much mojud thi."
4250,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : gunah sey tauba karney wala us shakhs ki tarah (ho jata) hai jis ka koi gunah nahin."
4251,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Adam (Alaihissalam) key sab betey khata-kaar hain aur behtareen khata kaar wo hain jo kasrat sey tauba kartey hain."
4252,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Maaqil (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main apney walid (Hazrat Maaqil bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu)) key sath Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa . mainey unhein suna , wo keh rahey they : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nadaamat tauba hai. merey walid sahab ney un sey kaha : kya aap ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey (baraahe-raast) suna hai ke aap ney farmaya : nadaamat tauba hai,? unhoney kaha : haan."
4253,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : be-shak Allah Taala us waqt tak bandey ki tauba qubul farmata rehta hai jab tak nazaa (jaan nikalne ke qareeb ka aalam) ka aalim taari na ho."
4254,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur bataya ke usney eik (ajnabi) aurat ka bosa ley liya hai. aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey us gunah ka kaffara daryaft karney laga. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney usey koi jawab na diya. phir Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farma di (وَأَقِمِ الصَّلَاةَ طَرَفَيِ النَّهَارِ وَزُلَفًا مِّنَ اللَّيْلِ padhi. إِنَّ الْحَسَنَاتِ يُذْهِبْنَ السَّيِّئَاتِ padhi. ذَٰلِكَ ذِكْرَىٰ لِلذَّاكِرِينَ),''din key kinaron mein aur raat ki ghadiyon mein namaz qaaim kijiye, be-shak nekiyan gunahon ko khatam kar deti hain, ye naseehat hai naseehat qubul karney walon key liye.'' us aadmi ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kya ye (riaayat) merey (hi) liye hai? aap ney farmaya : ye meri ummat key har us shakhs key liye hai jo is par amal karey."
4255,"Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) ney (apney shagrid Maamar sey) farmaya : ke main tujhey do ajeeb hadisein na sunaun? (pehli hadees ye hai jo) Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman ney Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik aadmi ney apni jaan par ziyadti ki (aur zindagi mein bahut gunah kiye), jab uski maut ka waqt aaya to usney apney beton ko wasiyat kartey huye kaha : jab main mar jaun to mujhey jala dena, phir mujhey (meri laash ko) pees kar, mujhey (meri raakh ko) hawa mein uda dena aur samandar mein baha dena. qism hai Allah ki ! agar Allah ney mujhey pakad liya to mujhey aisa azab dega jo kisi ko nahin diya hoga. un beton ney aisey hi kiya. Allah ney zamin sey kaha : jo tu ney liya hai hazir kar dey (aisey hi samandar sey bhi uski raakh key zarrey jama kar key usey zinda kar diya) achcha wo (zinda salaamat) khada tha. Allah ney us sey farmaya : tu ney jo kaam kiya hai, is par tujhey kis chiz ney aamada kiya? usney kaha : merey Rab ! terey khof ney. Allah Taala ney isi wajeh sey usey maaf kar diya."
4256,"Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) ney (dusri hadees bayan kartey huye) farmaya : aur mujhey Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey hadees sunai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik aurat eik billi ki wajeh sey jahannam mein chali gaee. usney isey baandh diya tha. na usey kuchh khaney ko diya, na usey chhoda ke zamin key keedey makodey kha leti yahan tak key wo (bhook sey) mar gaee. Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : (mainey ye do hadisein isliye sunai hain) taake koi (apni nekiyon par) bharosa na karey aur koi (Allah ki rehmat sey) mayus na ho."
4257,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Tabarak w Taala farmata hai : aey merey bando ! tum sab gunah karney waley ho, siwaye uskey jisey main mehfooz rakhun , isliye mujh sey bakhshish talab karo, main tumhein bakhsh dunga . tum mein sey jo koi ye yaqin rakhey ke main bakhshney ki qudrat rakhta hun, phir wo mujh sey meri qudrat key wastey sey bakhshish ki darkhaast karey to main uski maghfirat kar dunga . tum sab raah bhooley huye ho, siwaye uskey jisey main hidayat dun, chunanche mujh sey hidayat maango , main tumhein hidayat dunga . tum sab faqir (mohtaj aur muflis) ho, siwaye uskey jisey main ghani kar dun, lihaza mujh sey maango , main tumhein rizq dunga . agar tumharey zinda , faut shuda , pehley aur pichhley , tar aur khushk ikhattey ho kar merey bandon mein sey sab sey ziyada muttaqi insan jaisey dil waley bin jaeyn to us sey meri badshahat mein machchhar key par jitna bhi izafa nahin hoga . aur agar wo sab ikhattey ho kar merey bandon mein sey sab sey ziyada bad-nasib (aur bad-kar) bandey jaisey dil waley bin jaeyn , us sey meri badshahat mein machchhar key par jitni kami nahin aayegi. agar tumharey zinda, faut shuda , pehley aur pichhley , tar aur khushk ikhattey ho kar (mujh sey sawal karen aur) har maangney wala wo sab kuchh mang ley jiski wo (ziyada sey ziyada) tamanna kar sakta hai to us sey meri badshahat mein itni hi kami aayegi jaisey koi samandar key kinarey par jaaey aur us main eik soi dubo kar nikal ley, kyonkey main sakhi aur azmaton wala hun. meri ata kalam karna hai. jab main kisi chiz ka irada karun to usey sirf ye kehta hun : ho ja, wo ho jati hai."
4258,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : lazzaten khatam kar deney wali, yani maut, ko kasrat sey yad kiya karo."
4259,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha ke eik  Sahaba aaye (jo pehle nasraani the), unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko salam kiya, phir kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kon sa momin afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : jis ka akhlaq ziyada achchha ho. unhoney kaha : kon sa momin ziyada aql-mand hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo maut ko ziyada yad kartey hain aur uskey baad (key marhaley) key liye ziyada achchhi tayyari kartey hain, yehi aql mand hai hain."
4260,"Hazrat Abu Yaali Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aql-mand wo hai jo apna muhaasba karey aur maut key baad wali zindagi key liye amal karey. aur bewaqoof wo hai jo apney nafs ko uski khaahishat key peechhey laga dey (nafs ki khaahishat key mutabiq zindagi guzaarta hai). aur Allah sey (jhooti) umeeden wabasta karey (ye keh kar mutmain ho jaey ke Allah bahut bakhshney wala hai lekin amal aisey karey jis sey uski rehmat ki bajaey uska ghazab hasil ho)."
4261,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik nojawan key paas tashrif ley gaey jo qaribul-wafaat tha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya haal hai? usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! Allah sey (uski rehmat ki) ummid rakhta hun lekin apney gunahon sey dar bhi lagta hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis bandey key dil mein aisey moqe par ye dono cheezen (umeed aur khof) jama ho jaaeyn,  Allah Taala usey wo chiz deta hai jiski wo ummid rakhta hai aur us sey bacha leta hai jis sey wo darta hai."
4262,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qaribul-wafaat aadmi key paas farishtey aatey hain, agar aadmi nek ho to wo kehtey hain : nikal aey pak rooh jo pak jism mein thi. nikal, to qabile-tareef hai. tujhey khushkhabri ho rehmat aur khushbu ki (nematon ki) aur us Rab (sey mulaqat) ki jo naraz nahin. usey barabar isi tarah kaha jata hai yahan tak key wo ( jism sey) nikal aati hai. phir wo (farishtey) usey aasman ki taraf chadha ley jatey hain to uskey liye darwaza khol diya jata hai. kaha jata hai : ye kon hai? wo kehtey hain : falan shakhs hai. tab kaha jata hai : khush aamadeed ! pak rooh ko jo pak jism mein thi. dakhil ho ja, to qabile-tareef hai. aur tujhey khushkhabri ho, rehmat aur khushbu ki aur us Rab (sey mulaqat) ki jo naraz nahin. usey musalsal isi tarah kaha jata hai yahan tak key usey ley kar us aasman tak pahunchtey hain jis par Allah ki zaat aqdas hai. agar (marney wala) aadmi bura ho to farishta kehta hai : nikal aey khabees rooh jo gandey jism mein thi. nikal, to qabile-mazammat hai. tujhey khushkhabri ho kholtey huye pani ki, peep ki aur doosrey uskey mukhtalif azaabon ki. usey musalsal isi tarah kaha jata hai yahan tak key wo (jism sey) nikal aati hai. phir wo usey ley kar aasman ki taraf chadhtey hain to uskey liye darwaza nahin khultaa. kaha jata hai : ye kon hai? wo kehtey hain : falan hai. kaha jata hai : is napak rooh ko koi khush aamadeed nahin jo napak jism mein thi. wapis ho ja qabile-mazammat ho kar. terey liye aasman key darwazey nahin kholey jaaeyngey. tab usey aasman sey wapis bhej diya jata hai aur wo qabr mein aa pahunchti hai."
4263,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi shakhs ki maut kisi khas jagah par aana muqaddar hoti hai, uski (koi dunyawi) zarurat usey wahan ley jati hai. jab wo apney aakhiri qadam tak pahunchta hai to Allah Taala usey faut kar leta hai. qiyamat key din zamin kaheygi : merey Malik ! tu ney merey paas jo amanat rakhi thi, wo ye (hazir) hai."
4264,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah sey mulaqat pasand karta hai, Allah bhi us sey milna pasand karta hai. aur jo shakhs Allah sey mulaqat napasand karta hai, Allah bhi us sey mulaqat napasand karta hai. arz kiya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! maut ko napasand karney mein Allah ki mulaqat sey naa-pasandeedgi ka izhar hai. aur hum sab (taba'i tor par) maut ko napasand kartey hain (to phir najat kaisey hogi ?). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye baat nahin, us sey maut key waqt ki kaifiyat murad hai. jab (bandey ko) Allah ki rehmat aur maghfirat ki khush khabri di jati hai, wo Allah sey mulaqat karna pasand karta hai, tab Allah bhi us sey mulaqat karna pasand karta hai (aur us sey khush hota) hai. aur jab (kisi bandey ko) Allah key azab ki basharat di jaey, wo Allah sey mulaqat karna pasand nahin karta (marney sey ghabraataa hai), Allah bhi us sey mulaqat karna pasand nahin karta."
4265,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi aadmi nazil honey wali musibat ki wajeh sey maut ki tamanna na karey. agar wo maut ki tamanna zarur karna hi chahey to yun kahey : (اللَّهُمَّ أَحْيِنِي مَا كَانَتْ الْحَيَاةُ خَيْرًا لِي وَتَوَفَّنِي إِذَا كَانَتْ الْوَفَاةُ خَيْرًا لِي), ''aey Allah ! mujhey us waqt tak zinda rakh jab tak merey liye zindagi behtar ho. aur mujhey us waqt faut karna jab merey liye wafat behtar ho.''"
4266,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : insan ki har chiz boseedah ho (kar mitti mein mil) jati hai, siwaye eik haddi key, wo reedh ki haddi ka aakhiri mohra hai. qiyamat key din usi sey takhleeq shuru hogi."
4267,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Haani Barbari (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) jab kisi qabr key paas khadey hotey to itna rotey ke daadhi tar ho jati . kisi ney kaha : aap jannat aur jahannam ka zikr kartey hain. to aap ko ronaa nahin aata aur is (qabr) ko dekh kar rotey hain (iski kya wajeh hai?). unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qabr aakhirat ki pehli manzil hai. agar aadmi is sey najat paa gaya to baad waley marhale is sey aasan hongey. agar is sey najat na paa saka to baad key marhale is sey ziyada dushwaar hongey. wo bayan kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey jo bhi manzar kabhi dekha hai, qabr us sey ziyada holnaak hai."
4268,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maiyat qabr mein pahunch jati hai to nek aadmi ko qabr mein (utha kar) bitha diya jata hai. usey koi ghabrahat aur pareshani nahin hoti . usey kaha jata hai : to kis chiz mein tha? wo kehta hai : Islam mein . kaha jata hai : ye aadmi kon hai? wo kehta hai : Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah key Rasool , hamarey paas Allah key yahan sey wazeh dalaeyl ley kar aaye to hamney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki tasdeeq ki. kaha jata hai : tu ney Allah ko dekha hai? wo kehta hai : koi is qabil nahin ke (duniya mein) Allah ko dekh sakey . tab uskey liye jahannam ki taraf eik dareecha khola jata hai. wo dekhta hai ke aag aag ko tod phod rahi hai. usey kaha jata hai : dekh Allah ney tujhey kis chiz sey bacha liya hai, phir uskey liye jannat ki taraf dareecha khola jata hai, wo uski aab aur taab aur uski nematen dekhta hai. usey kaha jata hai : ye tera thikana hai. aur usey kaha jata hai : yaqin par to tha aur usi par teri wafat hui aur usi par to uthaya jaeyga Insha-Allah. burey aadmi ko qabr mein utha kar bithaya jata hai to wo ghabraayaa huwa aur bad-hawas hota hai. usey kaha jata hai : to kis chiz mein tha? wo kehta hai : malum nahin. usey kaha jata hai (teri taraf mab-us honey) bheja jaane (wala) ye aadmi kon hai? wo kehta hai : (mujhey malum nahin) mainey logon ko eik baat kehtey suna tha wo mainey bhi keh di. tab uskey liye jannat ki taraf eik dareecha khola jata hai, usey uski aab aur taab aur uski nematen nazar aati hain. usey kaha jata hai : dekh Allah ney tujhey kis chiz sey mehroom kar diya . phir uskey liye jahannam ki taraf dareecha khola jata hai. wo usey dekhta hai ke aag aag ko tod phod rahi hai. aur usey kaha jata hai : ye tera thikana hai. to (zindagi mein bhi) shak par tha aur isi haalat mein mar gaya aur usi par to uthaya jaaeyga. Insha-Allah."
4269,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye aayat azaabe-qabr key barey mein nazil hui hai : (يُثَبِّتُ اللَّهُ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا بِالْقَوْلِ الثَّابِتِ),''emaan walon ko Allah Taala pakki baat key sath mazbut rakhta hai.'' us sey kaha jata hai : tera Rab kon hai?  wo kehta hai : mera Rab Allah hai. aur (doosrey sawal key jawab mein kehta hai : ) merey Nabi Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain. isi liye Allah Taala ney farmaya : (يُثَبِّتُ اللَّهُ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا بِالْقَوْلِ الثَّابِتِ فِي الْحَيَاةِ الدُّنْيَا وَفِي الْآخِرَةِ),''emaan walon ko Allah Taala pakki baat key sath mazbut rakhta hai duniya ki zindagi mein bhi aur aakhirat mein bhi.''"
4270,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs faut ho jata hai to usey subh aur Sham uska thikana dikhaya jata hai. agar wo jannati hai to jannat ka thikana dikhaya jata hai aur agar jahannami hai to jahannam ka thikana dikhaya jata hai. kaha jata hai : ye tera thikana hai yahan tak key tujhey qiyamat key din (qabr sey) uthaya jaey.
4271,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Kaab Ansari (Rahimahullah) apney walid Hazrat Kaab bin Malik Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin ki jaan eik perindey ki surat mein jannat key darakhton sey (phal) khati hai yahan tak key uthney key din (qiyamat ko) dobara apney jism mein chali jaeygi."
4272,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab maiyat qabr mein pahunchti hai to usey suraj doobta nazar aata hai. wo aankhen malta huwa uth bethta hai aur kehta hai : mujhey chhodo namaz padh leney do."
4273,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : soor phoonkney waley dono farishton key haathon mein do narsinghey (bigul) hain. wo nazar utha utha kar dekhtey hain ke kab unhein (phunk maarney ka) hukm diya jaaeyga."
4274,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Madina key bazar main eik Yahudi ney (baat cheet key doran mein) keh diya : qism hai us zaat ki jisney Musa ko muntakhab farma kar insanon par fazilat di ! eik Ansari Sahaba ney haath uthaya aur us (yahudi) key munh par thappad maar diya. aur kaha : to ye alfaz kehta hai, halanke hamarey andar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mojud hain? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye baat batai gaee to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah farmata hai : (وَنُفِخَ فِي الصُّورِ فَصَعِقَ مَنْ فِي السَّمَاوَاتِ وَمَنْ فِي الْأَرْضِ إِلَّا مَنْ شَاءَ اللَّهُ ثُمَّ نُفِخَ فِيهِ أُخْرَى فَإِذَا هُمْ قِيَامٌ يَنْظُرُونَ),'aur soor mein phunk maari jaaeygi to aasman aur zamin waley sab be-hosh ho jaaeyngey magar jisey Allah chahey, phir is mein dobara phunk maari jaaeygi to wo eik dam khadey ho kar dekhney lagengey.'' sab sey pehley sar uthaney wala main hunga. achcha main dekhunga ke Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) arsh key paayon mein sey eik paaey ko thaamey khadey hain. malum nahin ke unhoney mujh sey pehley (hosh mein aa kar) sar utha liya hoga ya wo un afrad mein shamil hongey jinhein Allah ney mustasna (khaas) qarar diya hai. aur jo shakhs kahey ke main Yunus bin Matti (Alaihissalam) sey afzal hun usney jhoot kaha."
4275,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par tashrif farma ho kar ye farmatey huye suna : Jabbaar (Allah Ta'alaa) aasmano aur zaminon ko apney haath mein ley ley ga. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (ye farmatey huye) apna haath band kiya, phir usey kholney aur band karney lagey . phir farmaaeyga : main Jabbaar (zabardast) hun. main badshah hun, kahan hain (duniya key naam nihad) Jabbaar? kahan hain mutakabbir? (ye farmatey huye) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (josh key sath) daain baain harkat farmatey they yahan tak key mainey dekha ke member nichey tak harkat kar raha tha. aur main (dil mein) kehney laga : kahin wo (member) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ley kar gir na padey?"
4276,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! qiyamat key din log kis haalat mein uthengey? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nangey paon, nangey badan, mainey kaha : aur aurten : farmaya : aurten bhi. mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! hamein sharam nahin aayegi? farmaya : Aaisha ! maamla us sey ziyada sakht hai ke koi kisi ko dekhey (apni apni pareshani mein kisi ko itna hosh hi kahan hoga ke wo dekhta phirey doosrey nangey hain ya libas pehney huye hain)."
4277,"Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din logon ki teen paishiyaan hongi. do paishiyon mein to behes mubaahasa bhi hoga. aur mazraten bhi pesh ki jaeyngi. teesri peshi mein aamal-namey ud kar haathon mein aa jaaeyngey. koi usey apney daain haath mein lega aur koi baaein hath mein."
4278,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is aayate-mubaarka ki tilawat farmaai : (يَوْمَ يَقُومُ النَّاسُ لِرَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ ),''jis din log Rabul-Aalameen key samney khadey hongey. aur farmaya : aadmi aadhey kanon tak apney paseeney mein khada hoga."
4279,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey daryaft kiya ke Allah Taala farmata hai : (يَوْمَ تُبَدَّلُ الْأَرْضُ غَيْرَ الْأَرْضِ وَالسَّمَاوَاتُ),'jis din ye zamin kisi aur zamin sey badal di jaeygi aur aasman bhi.'' us waqt insan kahan hongey? aap ney farmaya : pul siraat par."
4280,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pul-siraat ko jahannam key ooper rakha jaaeyga. is par kaantey hongey, jaisey sa'daan key kaantay. phir log guzrengey. kuchh sahih salaamat bach niklengey, kuchh naqis jism waley ho kar aakhir kaar bach niklengey. phir (nateeja ye hoga ke) koi najat paa jaaeyga, koi wahan rok liya jaeyga aur koi sar key bal is mein ja gireyga."
4281,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey ummid hai ke Badr aur hudaibiya mein hazir honey wala koi aadmi In-sha-Allah jahannam mein nahin jaaeyga. Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya Allah Taala ney ye nahin farmaya : (وَإِنْ مِنْكُمْ إِلَّا وَارِدُهَا كَانَ عَلَى رَبِّكَ حَتْمًا مَقْضِيًّا),''tum mein sey har eik zarur is par pahunchney wala hai. ye aap key parwardigar key zimmey qataee tey shuda baat hai.'' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tu ney Allah Taala ka ye farman nahin suna : ( ثُمَّ نُنَجِّي الَّذِينَ اتَّقَوْا وَنَذَرُ الظَّالِمِينَ فِيهَا جِثِيًّا ),''phir hum perhez gaaron ko bacha leingey aur zalimon ko is mein ghutnon key bal gira huwa chhod dengey.''"
4282,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din tum merey paas (hoz par) aaogey to wuzu ki wajeh sey tumharey chehrey aur haath paaon chamaktey hongey. ye meri ummat ki alamat hai jo kisi aur ummat ko hasil nahin."
4283,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log eik khemey mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum is baat sey khush ho ke tumhari tadaad tamam jannatiyon ki chothai ho? hamney kaha : ji haan. farmaya : kya tum is baat sey khush ho ke tumhari tadaad tamam jannatiyon ki tihai ho? hamney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! mujhey ummid hai ke tumhaari tadaad tamam jannatiyon ka nisf (aadhi) hogi. uski wajeh ye hai ke jannat mein sirf musalman hi dakhil hoga. aur mushrikon key muqabley mein tumhari tadaad aisey hai jaisey siyah bail ki jald par eik safed baal ya surkh bail ki jald par eik siyah baal."
4284,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (qiyamat key din) eik Nabi aayega, uskey sath sirf do aadmi hongey (jo is par eman laaye). aur eik Nabi aayega uskey sath teen aadmi hongey. (isi tarah tamam nabiyon key sath) ziyada aur kam afrad hongey. Nabi sey kaha jaeyga : kya tum ney apni qom ko (Allah key ehkam)  pahuncha diye they? wo Nabi farmaaeyga : haan. uski qom ko bula kar kaha jaeyga : kya usney tumhein (Allah key ehkam) pahuncha diye they? wo kahengey : nahin. (Nabi sey) kaha jaeyga : aap ka gawah kon hai? wo farmaeyga : Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur un ki ummat. Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ummat sey kaha jaeyga : kya is Nabi ney (apni qom ko Allah key) ehkam pahunchaey they? momin kahengey : haan. Allah Taala farmaeyga : tumhein kya maloom? momin kahengey : hamin hamarey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khabar di thi ke anbiyaae-kiraam ney (apni-apni ummat ko Allah key ehkam) pahunchaey they. hamney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sachcha taslim kiya. Allah key is farman ka yehi matlab hai(وَكَذَٰلِكَ جَعَلْنَاكُمْ أُمَّةً وَسَطًا لِّتَكُونُوا شُهَدَاءَ عَلَى النَّاسِ وَيَكُونَ الرَّسُولُ عَلَيْكُمْ شَهِيدًا ),''aur (jaisay hamney tumhein hidayat di) isi tarah hamney tumhein afzal ummat banaya taake tum logon par gawah ho jaao, aur Rasool tum par gawah hon.''"
4285,"Hazrat Rifaa (bin Araaba) Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath safar sey wapis aaye to aap ney farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! jo aadmi eman laye, phir sidhi raah par qaaim rahey, usey zarur jannat mein pahunchaaya jaaeyga. aur mujhey ummid hai ke wo log (dusri ummaton key jannati) us waqt tak dakhil nahin hongey jab tak tum aur tumhaari nek auladen jannat key gharon mein na pahunch jaaeyn. aur merey Rab ney mujh sey wada kiya hai ke meri ummat mein sey sattar hazar afrad ko baghair hisab key jannat mein dakhil karega."
4286,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Sudayyi bin Ajlan) Baahli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey Rab ney mujh sey wada kiya hai ke meri ummat mein sey sattar hazar afrad ko jannat mein dakhil karega, jin sey na koi hisab liya jaeyga aur na unhein koi azab diya jaeyga. har hazar key sath sattar hazar aur hongey aur (mazeed) merey Shaan waley Rab ki teen lappein."
4287,"Hazrat Behaz bin Hakim apney walid sey aur wo unkey dada (Hazrat Muawiya bin Haida Qushairi (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din hamarey samet sattar qomen (ummaten) hongi. hum un mein sey sab sey aakhiri aur sab sey afzal (ummat) hongey."
4288,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Haida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum ney sattar ummaton ki tadaad ko pura kiya hai. un mein sey tum sab sey afzal aur Allah key yahan moazziz ho."
4289,"Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (maidane-mehshar mein) ehale-jannat ki eik sau bees safein hongi. un mein sey assi (80) is ummat ki hongi aur chaalis safein baqi tamam ummaton ki."
4290,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hum aakhiri ummat hain aur hamara hisab sab sey pehley hoga. kaha jaeyga : kahan hai Ummi ummat aur unka Nabi? to hum baad mein aaney waley, (jannat mein dakhley key lihaz sey) sab sey muqaddam hain."
4291,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din jab Allah Taala tamam makhluqat ko jama farma lega to Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ummat ko sajda karney ki ijazat di jaeygi . wo Allah ko taweel sajda kerengey . phir kaha jaeyga : apney sar uthaao hamney tumhari tadaad key mutabiq jahannamiyon ko tumhara fidya bana diya hai."
4292,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is ummat par rehmat nazil ki gaee hai. is par azab khud uskey haath sey aayega. jab qiyamat ka din hoga to har musalman ko eik mushrik diya jaeyga aur kaha jaeyga : ye jahannam sey bachao key liye tera fidya hai."
4293,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ki eik sau rahmatein hain jin mein sey eik rehmat usney tamam makhluqat mein taqseem ki hai. isi (rehmat) ki wajeh sey wo eik doosrey par reham kartey hain. usi ki wajeh sey eik doosrey par shafqat kartey hain. usi ki wajeh sey jangli janwer apney bachon par shafqat kartey hain. usney ninniyanaawey rahmatein rakh chhodi hain. jin sey qiyamat key din wo apney bandon par reham kerega."
4294,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney jis din aasmano aur zamin ko paida kiya to sau rahmatein bhi paida farmaaeen. un mein sey eik rehmat zamin mein rakhi. usi (rehmat) ki wajeh sey maa apney bachchey par shafqat karti hai aur haiwaanaat aur perindey eik doosrey par shafqat kartey hain. us (Allah) ney aur ninnanwey rahmaton ko qiyamat tak key liye muakhkhar farma diya. jab qiyamat ka din hoga, Allah Taala us eik rehmat key sath unhein puri (sau rahmatein) kar dega."
4295,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bilashuba Allah ney jab makhluq ko paida farmaya to apney haath sey apney liye ye likh liya (apney liye ye zaruri thehra liya : ) meri rehmat merey ghazab par ghalib hogi."
4296,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main eik gadhey par sawar tha ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas sey guzrey aur farmaya : Muaz ! kya tujhey malum hai ke bandon key zimmey Allah ka kya haq hai aur Allah key zimmey bandon ka kya haq hai? mainey kaha : Allah aur uska Rasool behtar jantey hain. aap ney farmaya : bandon par Allah ka haq ye hai ke wo usi ki ibadat karen aur uskey sath kisi chiz ko (ibadat mein) shareek na karen. aur Allah par bandon ka haq ye hai ke jab wo ye kaam karen to unhein azab na dey."
4297,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log kisi ghazwey mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. hamara guzar kuchh logon key paas sey huwa to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kon log ho? unhoney kaha : hum musalman hain. eik aurat tanur mein endhan dal (kar usey dahka) rahi thi. aur uskey paas uska beta tha, jab tanur ki (aag ki) lipat ooper aati, wo bachchey ko peechhey kar leti. wo aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha : aap Allah key Rasool hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan. usney kaha : merey maa baap aap par qurban ! kya Allah Taala sab reham karney walon sey ziyada reham karney wala nahin? aap ney farmaya : kyon nahin, usney kaha : kya Allah Taala apney bandon par us sey ziyada reham karney wala nahin jis qadr maa apney bachchey par karti hai? aap ney farmaya : kyon nahin? usney kaha : maa to apney bachchey ko aag mein nahin phainkti. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sar jhuka liya aur roney lagey, phir sar Mubarak utha kar uski taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : Allah Taala apney kisi bandey ko azab nahin deta, siwaye us sarkash adiyal key jo Allah sey sarkashi karta hai. aur لا الٰہ الا اللہ kehney sey inkar kar deta hai."
4298,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jahannam main to bad nasib hi jaeyga. arz kiya gaya . Allah key Rasool ! bad nasib kon hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Allah ki farman-bardari ka koi amal nahin kiya aur Allah ki nafarmani wala koi amal nahin chhoda."
4299,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ( هُوَ أَهْلُ التَّقْوَىٰ وَأَهْلُ الْمَغْفِرَةِ ),''wo usi laaiq hai ke us sey daren aur is laaiq bhi ke wo bakhshey.'' phir farmaya : Allah Taala farmata hai : main is laaiq hun ke mujh sey dara jaaey , aur merey sath koi doosra mabood na banaya jaey . jo shakhs merey sath doosra mabood bananey sey dar gaya to main is laaiq hun ke usey bakhsh dun. dusri sanad sey Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke is aayat key barey mein : ( هُوَ أَهْلُ التَّقْوَىٰ وَأَهْلُ الْمَغْفِرَةِ ) Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara parwardigar farmata hai : ''main is laaiq hun ke mujh sey dara jaey aur merey sath kisi doosrey ko shareek na banaya jaey.''aur jo shakhs is baat sey dar gaya (aur perhez kiya) ke merey sath shareek karey to main is laaiq hun ke usey bakhsh dun."
4300,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din merey eik ummati ko sab makhluq key samney pukar kar talab kiya jaeyga. uskey ninnanwey rajister khol diye jaaeyngey. har rajister itna bada hoga jahan tak nigah pahunchey. phir Allah Taala farmaeyga : kya to is (tamam rikard) mein sey kisi chiz (kisi gunah) ka inkar karta hai? wo kaheyga : nahin, merey Malik ! Allah Taala farmaeyga : kya merey (muqarrar kiye huye) muhafiz kaatibon ney tujh par zulm kiya hai. (ke teri nekiyan na likhi hun ya gunah ziyada likh diye hon)? phir farmaeyga : kya in (gunahon) key ilawa teri koi neki bhi hai? wo shakhs khof-zada ho jaaeyga aur kaheyga : nahin. Allah Taala farmaeyga : kyon nahin, hamarey paas teri nekiyan bhi hain aur aaj tujh par koi zulm nahin hoga, chunanche us (key amal) ka eik (kaghaz ka chhota sa) purzaa laya jaeyga. is par likha hoga : ( أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَأَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ ), ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain.'' banda kaheyga : ya Rab ! un rajistaron key muqabley mein ye purzaa kya (haisiyat rakhta) hai? Allah Taala farmaeyga : aaj tujh par zulm nahin kiya jaaeyga, chunanche wo tamam rajister eik paldey mein rakhey jaaeyngey aur wo purzaa eik paldey mein rakha jaaeyga. wo tamam rajister ooper uth jaaeyngey aur wo purza bhari Sabit hoga.(Raavi hadees, Imam Ibne-Maja key ustaad) Muhammad bin Yahyaa ney kaha : (hadees mein mazkur lafz) بطاقہ sey murad رقعہ hai. Misr waley رقعہ ko بطاقہ kehtey hain."
4301,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mera eik hoz hai jo Kaba aur Baitul-Maqdis key darmiyan (ki masafat key barabar wasee) hai. (uska pani) doodh ki tarah safed hai. uskey bartan sitaron ki tadaad ki tarah (be-shumar) hain. aur qiyamat key din merey ummati sab Nabiyon (Aleh.) key umattiyon sey ziyada hongey."
4302,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mera hoz ila sey ley kar adn tak key fasley sey ziyada taweel aur areez hai. qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! uskey bartan sitaron ki tadaad sey ziyada hain. us (key pani) ka rang doodh sey ziyada safed aur (zaiqa) shehad sey ziyada mitha hai. qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! main logon ko us sey hataaunga jis tarah aadmi apney hoz sey begaaney oonton ko haank deta hai. arz kiya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! kya aap hamein pehchan leingey? aap ney farmaya : haan, tum merey paas (hoz par) aaoey to wuzu key nishan sey tumharey chehrey aur haath paaon chamak rahey hongey. ye alamat tumharey siwa kisi aur (ummat) ki nahin hogi."
4303,"Hazrat Abu-Salaam Habshi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mujhey Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ney bulaya main (jald pahunchney ki gharz sey) daak key ghodon par sawar ho kar aaya. jab main khidmat mein hazir huwa to unhon (Umar bin abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah)) ney farmaya : Abu-Salaam ! hamari wajeh sey aap ko is sawari ki mashaqqat uthaani padi. mainey kaha : ji haan, Ameerul-mominin ! farmaya : qism hai. Allah ki ! main aap ko mashaqqat mein nahin dalna chahta tha lekin mujhey malum huwa tha ke aap Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key azad karda Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey hoz key barey main eik hadees riwayat kartey hain. mainey chaha ke aap sey baraahe-raast wo hadees sunoon. Abu-Salaam (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mujhey Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) Mola Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hadees sunai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mera hoz adn sey ley kar ila tak (ki masafat jitna taweel aur areez) hai. wo doodh sey ziyada safed aur shehad sey ziyada mitha hai. uskey piyaley aasman key sitaron ki tadaad ki tarah (be-shumar) hain. jo is mein sey eik baar pani pi leyga, usey uskey baad kabhi piyas nahin lageygi. hoz par merey paas sab sey pehley wo gharib Muhajir aayengey jinkey kapdey mailey aur sar  bikhrey hue hongey. jo naaz aur nemat mein pali hui aurton sey nikah nahin kartey aur unkey liye darwazey nahin kholey jatey. Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ro padey yahan tak key un ki daadhi Mubarak (aansuon sey) tar ho gaee. phir farmaya : lekin mainey to naaz aur nemat wali aurton sey nikah kiya hai, aur merey liye darwazey kholey gaey. ab zarur ye hoga ke main pehney huye kapdey nahin dhounga jab tak mailey na ho jaaeyn, aur sar mein tel nahin dalunga jab tak baal na bikhar jaeyn."
4304,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey hoz key do kinaron key darmiyan itna fasla hai, jaisey San'aa aur Madina Munawra key darmiyan ya jaisey Madina Munawra aur Amaan key darmiyan."
4305,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is (hoz) mein aasman key sitaron ki tadaad ki tarah soney aur chaandi key jag hongey."
4306,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qabristaan mein tashrif ley gaey aur qabristaan (mein dafan huey afrad) ko salam kartey huye farmaya : (السَّلَامُ عَلَيْكُمْ دَارَ قَوْمٍ مُؤْمِنِينَ وَإِنَّا إِنْ شَاءَ اللَّهُ تَعَالَى بِكُمْ لَاحِقُونَ), ''aey momin logon ki basti key rehney walon ! tum par salamti ho, hum bhi Insha-Allah tum sey milney waley hain.'' phir aap ney farmaya : hamari khahish thi ke hum apney bhaiyon ko dekh saktey. Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya hum aap key bhai nahin? aap ney farmaya : tum to merey sathi aur Sahaba ho. merey bhai to wo hain jo merey baad ayengey. aur main hoz par tumhara pesh-rau hunga. Sahaba ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap ki ummat key jo log abhi (duniya mein) nahin aaye, aap (qiyamat key din) unhein kis tarah pahchaaneingey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye batao agar kisi key panj-kaliyaan ghodey (doosron key) mukammal tor par kaley ghodon mein mil jaeyn to kya wo unhein pehchan na ley ga? unhoney kaha : kyon nahin ( pehchan ley ga). aap ney farmaya : ye log ( Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ummati)  qiyamat key din aaeyngey to wuzu key asar sey unkey chehrey aur haath paon safed hongey. aur farmaya : main hoz par tumhara pesh-rau hunga. phir farmaya : kuchh afrad ko merey hoz sey door hataayaa jaaeyga jis tarah gum-shuda (paraaey) oont ko door hataayaa jata hai, chunanche main unhein aawaz dunga (idhar aa jao). to kaha jaeyga : unhoney aap key baad (apni haalat) tabdeel kar li thi. aur apni ediyon par phir gaey they. tab main kahunga : door raho ! door raho !."
4307,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har Nabi ki eik maqbool dua hoti hai aur har Nabi ney wo dua jaldi (duniya mein) mang li. mainey apni dua ko ummat key haq mein shafaat key liye chhupa kar rakha huwa tha. ye (dua) ummat key har us shakhs ko nasib hogi. jo Allah key sath kisi chiz ko shareek na kartey huye faut hoga."
4308,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main aulade-Adam ka sardar hun aur koi fakhr nahin. qiyamat key din sab sey pehley meri qabr shaqq hogi aur koi fakhr nahin. sab sey pehley mein shafaat karunga aur sab sey pehley meri shafaat qubul ki jaeygi aur koi fakhr nahin. qiyamat key din hamd ka jhandaa merey haath mein hoga aur koi fakhr nahin."
4309,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo jahannami jo jahannam key asal mustahiq (aur hamesha is mein rehney waley) hain, wo to is mein na mareingey na jieingey lekin kuchh log jinhein unkey gunahon ya ghaltiyon ki wajeh sey jahannam pakad leygi, wo unhein eik baar faut kar degi yahan tak key jab wo (jal kar) koila ho jaeyngey to unkey haq mein shafaat ki ijazat mil jaaeygi, chunanche unhein giroh giroh kar key laya jaeyga aur jannat ki nehron (key kinaron) par bikher diya jaeyga, phir kaha jaeyga : jannat walo ! in par pani dalo. (pani dalney sey) wo is tarah ugengey jis tarah sailab ki laee hui mitti mein dana ugta hai. (ye sun kar) haazirin mein sey eik sahab ney kaha : lagta hai Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sehraai maidaanon mein rehtey rahey hain."
4310,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din meri shafaat meri ummat key kabeera (badey) gunahon key murtakib (mujrim) afrad key liye (bhi) hogi."
4311,"Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey shafaat aur aadhi ummat key jannat key dakhiley mein sey koi eik chiz muntakhab karney ki ijazat di gaee to mainey shafaat ko muntakhab kar liya kyonkey ye ziyada afrad ko shamil karney wali aur ziyada kifaayat karney wali hai. kya tumhara ye khayal hai ke ye perhez gaaron key liye hogi? nahin, balke ye gunah gaaron, khata-kaaron aur (gunahon mein) luthdey huye logon key liye hogi."
4312,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din momin jama hongey, phir unhein ilhaam hoga ya farmaya : wo fikr-mand hongey, (hadees key Raavi) Saeed ko shak huwa hai. tab wo kahengey : kaash! hum apney Rab key darbar mein (kisi ki) sifarish pesh karen to wo hamein us jagah sey (hataa kar key) rahat nasib farmaaey, chunanche wo Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam) key paas jaeynge aur kahengey : aap Adam hain jo sab insanon key walid hain. aap ko Allah ney apney haath sey paida farmaya aur uskey farishton ney aap ko sajda kiya, lihaza aap hamarey liye apney Rab sey shafaat kijiye ke hamein is maqam sey rahat nasib farmaaey. wo kahengey main is qabil nahin aur apney us gunah ka zikr aur shikayat kerengey jo un sey sarzad ho gaya tha. (jis darkht sey mana kiya gaya tha, uska phal kha liya tha). wo apney Rab sey sharam mehsus kerengey. (aur kahengey) Nuh (Alaihissalam) key paas jaao. wo pehley Rasool hain jinhein Allah Taala ney ehale zamin ki taraf (Nabi bana kar) bheja. log unkey paas aayengey, wo kahengey : main is qabil nahin hun. wo is baat ka zikr kar key sharam mehsus kerengey ke unhoney apney Rab sey aisa sawal kiya tha jiski haqiqat ka unhein ilm nahin tha. (wo kahengey : ) lekin tum Allah key Khaleel Hazrat Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) key paas jaao. log unkey paas jaaeyngey, wo farmaeyngey : main is qabil nahin, lekin tum Musa (Alaihissalam) key paas jaao. wo Allah key aisey bandey hain jin sey Allah ney (baraahe-raast) kalam farmaya aur unhein Torat ata farmaai. log unkey paas jaeyngey to wo farmaeyngey : main is qabil nahin. wo eik aadmi key be-gunah qatl karney ka zikr farmaain gey. (wo kahengey) lekin Esa (Alaihissalam) key paas jaao. wo Allah key bandey, uskey Rasool, uska kalima aur uski rooh hain. log unkey paas jaeyngey, wo farmaeyngey : main is qabil nahin. lekin tum Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas jaao. wo Allah key aisey bandey hain jinkey agley-pichhley gunah Allah ney maaf farma diye hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : log merey paas aayengey, main chal padoonga. eik riwayat mein hai : main mominon ki do safon key darmiyan sey guzar kar jaaunga. aur farmaya : main apney Rab key paas hazir honey ki ijazat talab karunga, mujhey ijazat mil jaeygi. jab main apney Rab ko dekhunga to sajdey mein gir jaaunga. Allah Taala jab tak chahega, mujhey (sajdey mein) rehney dega. phir kaha jaeyga : Muhammad ! sar uthaaiye ! baat kijiye, aap ki baat suni jaeygi. sawal kijiye, aap ko diya jaeyga. shafaat kijiye , aap ki shafaat qubul ki jaeygi. tab main Allah ki wo tareefen karunga jo wo mujhey sikhaeyga, phir shafaat karunga, (chunanche) merey liye eik had muqarrar kar di jaeygi, Allah un logon ko (jinkey haq mein shafaat ki ijazat di hogi) jannat mein dakhil kar dega, phir main dusri baar jaaunga. jab main apney Rab ko dekhunga to sajdey mein gir jaaunga. Allah Taala jab tak chahega mujhey (sajdey mein) rehney dega. phir mujhey kaha jaeyga. Muhammad ! sar uthaaiye ! baat kijiye , aap ki baat suni jaeygi . sawal kijiye , aap ko diya jaeyga, shafaat kijiye . aap ki shafaat qubul ki jaeygi . tab main sar utha kar Allah ki wo tareefen karunga jo wo mujhey sikhaeyga, phir main shafaat karunga, (chunanche) merey liye eik had muqarrar kar di jaeygi, Allah un logon ko (jinkey haq mein shafaat ki ijazat di hogi) jannat mein dakhil kar dega. phir main teesri baar jaaunga. jab main apney Rab ko dekhunga to sajdey mein gir jaaunga, Allah Taala jab tak chahega mujhey (sajdey mein) rehney dega, phir mujhey kaha jaeyga : Muhammad ! sar uthaaiye ! baat kijiye , aap ki baat suni jaeygi. sawal kijiye , aap ko diya jaeyga. shafaat kijiye , aap ki shafaat qubul ki jaeygi. tab main sar utha kar Allah ki wo tareefen karunga jo wo mujhey sikhaeyga. phir main shafaat karunga, (chunanche) merey liye eik had muqarrar kar di jaaeygi aur Allah un logon ko jannat mein dakhil kar dega (jinkey haq mein shafaat ki ijazat di hogi). phir main chauthi baar jaaunga aur arz karunga : merey Rab ! (jahannam mein) sirf wohi baqi reh gaey hain jinhein Quran ney rok diya hai. ye hadees bayan karney key baad Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they : hamein Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney hadees sunai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo aadmi jahannam sey nikal aayega jisney لا الٰہ الا اللہ kaha , aur uskey dil mein jau key wazan key barabar bhalai (emaan) hai. aur jahannam sey wo bhi nikal aayega jisney لا الٰہ الا اللہ kaha aur uskey dil mein gehun key eik daney key barabar bhalai (emaan) hai. aur jahannam sey wo bhi nikal aayega jisney لا الٰہ الا اللہ kaha, aur uskey dil main eik zarrey key wazan key barabar bhalai (emaan) hai."
4313,"Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din teen qism key afrad shafaat kerengey : pehley anbiyaae-kiraam, phir ulama, phir shaheed."
4314,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab qiyamat ka din hoga to main nabiyon ka Imam, unka khateeb, aur un mein sey (pehley) shafaat karney wala hunga, aur koi fakhr nahin."
4315,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : yaqinan kuchh log meri shafaat ki wajeh sey jahannam sey niklengey, unhein jahannami kaha jaaeyga."
4316,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abu Jadaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat key eik aadmi ki shafaat ki wajeh sey qabila banu Tameem (ki tadaad) sey ziyada log jannat mein dakhil hongey. Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! wo aap key ilawa koi aur hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey ilawa (koi aur hai). Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaqeeq (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mainey kaha : kya ye hadees Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey aap ney khud suni hai? Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey khud suni hai."
4317,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum logon ko malum hai ke aaj raat merey Rab ney mujhey kis intikhaab ka haq inayat farmaya? hamney kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ko ziyada malum hai. aap ney farmaya : usney mujhey aadhi ummat key jannat mein dakhley aur shafaat mein sey koi eik chiz muntakhab (chun'ne) karney ka ikhtiyar diya. mainey shafaat ko muntakhab kar liya. hamney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! Allah sey dua kijiye ke hamein bhi shafaat paney walon mein shamil farma dey. aap ney farmaya : wo har musalman key liye hai."
4318,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhari ye aag jahannam ki aag key sattar hisson mein sey eik hissa hai. aur agar isey dobara pani key sath bujhaya na gaya hota to tum is sey faeyda na utha saktey. aur ye (duniya ki aag) Allah sey dua karti hai ke usey dobara jahannam mein na bheja jaey.
4319,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jahannam ney apney Rab sey shikayat kartey huye kaha : ya Rab ! merey eik hissey ney doosrey ko kha liya. Allah Taala ney uskey liye do saans muqarrar kar diye. eik saans sardi key mausam mein aur eik saans garmi key mausam mein. tumhein jab sakht sardi mehsus hoti hai to ye uski shadeed sardi ki wajeh sey hai. aur jab tumhein sakht garmi mehsus hoti hai to ye uski shadeed garmi ki wajeh sey hai."
4320,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jahannam (ki aag) eik hazar saal tak dehkaai gaee to wo safed ho gaee, phir hazar saal tak dehkaai gaee to wo surkh ho gaee, phir hazar saal tak dehkaai gaee to siyah ho gaee. (ab) wo taareek (andheri) raat ki tarah siyah hai."
4321,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din us kafir ko laya jaeyga jo duniya mein sab sey ziyada nematon wala tha (jis ki zindagi sab sey ziyada aesh aur ishrat, khushiyon aur nematon mein guzri). phir kaha jaaeyga : isey aag main eik ghota do. usey us main eik ghota diya jaeyga, phir kaha jaeyga : aey falan ! kya tujhey kabhi koi nemat (aur rahat) bhi hasil hui hai? wo kaheyga : nahin, mujhey (zindagi bhar) koi nemat (ya rahat) hasil nahin hui. aur us momin ko laya jaeyga jis par sab sey ziyada sakht museebatein aur aazmaaishein aaein. kaha jaeyga : usey jannat mein uski nematon ki eik jhalak dikha kar laao. usey jannat ki eik jhalak dikha kar laya jaeyga. aur kaha jaeyga : aey falan ! kya tujhey kabhi koi musibat aur aazmaaish bhi aai thi? wo kaheyga : mujhey to (zindagi bhar) kabhi koi musibat ya aazmaaish (aur takleef) nahin aai."
4322,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kafir ( jahannam mein , jismani tor par) bahut bada ho jaeyga yahan tak key uski daadh uhad pahad sey bhi badi ho jaeygi . aur uska jism uski daadh sey itna hi bada hoga jitna (duniya mein) kisi ka jism uski daadh sey bada hota hai."
4323,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Qais (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main eik raat Hazrat abu-Barda (Rahimahullah) key yahan thehraa. hamarey paas Hazrat Haris bin Aqeesh (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif ley aaye. us raat Hazrat Haris bin Aqeesh (Raziallahu anhu) ney hadees sunai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat mein wo fard bhi hai jiski shafaat ki wajeh sey qabila muzir (key afrad ki tadaad) sey ziyada afrad jannat mein dakhil hongey. aur meri ummat mein wo fard bhi hai jo jahannam mein itna bada ho jaeyga ke uska eik kona bin jaaeyga."
4324,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jahannamiyon par ronaa musallat kiya jaeyga, chunanche wo itna ro'ein gey ke unkey aansu khatam ho jaeyngey. phir wo khoon key aansu ro'eingey yahan tak key unkey chehron par khandaqon ki tarah nishan bin jaaeyngey. agar un (aansuon) mein kashtiyan chhodi jaeyn to wo bhi (aansuon ki nehar mein) bahney lagen."
4325,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aayate-mubaarka tilawat farmaai : ( يَاأَيُّهَا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا اتَّقُوا اللَّـهَ حَقَّ تُقَاتِهِ وَلَا تَمُوتُنَّ إِلَّا وَأَنتُم مُّسْلِمُونَ ),''aey eman walo ! Allah Taala sey itna daro, jitna us sey darney ka haq hai aur martey dam tak musalman hi rehna.'' phir farmaya : agar zaqqum ka eik qatra zamin par tapkaa diya jaey to duniya walon ki zindagi kharab kar dey, phir uska kya haal hoga jis ka khana uskey siwa kuchh nahin hoga?"
4326,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aag Adam (Alaihissalam) key betey ko kha jaeygi, siwaye sajdon key nishan key. Allah Taala ney aag par sajdey ka nishan khana haram farma diya hai."
4327,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din maut ko la kar pul-siraat par khada kar diya jaeyga, phir kaha jaeyga : jannat walo ! wo dartey dartey jhaankeingey. unhein khof hoga ke unhein us jagah (jannat) sey nikal na diya jaey jahan wo mojud hain. phir kaha jaeyga : jahannam walo ! wo khush ho kar jhaankein gey, unhein (is ummid ki wajeh sey) khushi hogi ke unhein is jagah sey nikal liya jaeyga jahan wo mojud hain. (phir) kaha jaeyga : kya tum us chiz ko pehchantey ho? wo kahengey : haan, ye maut hai. phir Allah key hukm sey us (maut) ko pal-siraat par zibeh kar diya jaeyga aur dono girohon sey keh diya jaeyga : tum jis chiz mein ho, usi mein hamesha rahogey. is mein kabhi maut nahin aayegi."
4328,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah farmata hai : mainey apney nek bandon key liye wo kuchh tayyar kar rakha hai jisey kisi aankh ney dekha hai na kisi kaan ney suna aur na kisi insan key dil mein uska khayal tak aaya hai. Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : jin nematon aur lazzaton ki ittilaa Allah Taala ney tumhein dey di hai wo chhodo (is hadees mein wo murad nahin balke un sey azeem tar inaamat murad hain). chaho to ye aayat padh lo. (فَلَا تَعْلَمُ نَفْسٌ مَّا أُخْفِيَ لَهُم مِّن قُرَّةِ أَعْيُنٍ جَزَاءً بِمَا كَانُوا يَعْمَلُونَ ),''koi nafs nahin janta ke unkey aamaal key badley mein unkey liye aakhon ki thandak ki kon-kon si cheezen poshida rakhi gaee hain.''Hazrat Abu-Saaleh (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Hazrat Abu-Hurera is aayat mein (مِّن قُرَّاتِ أَعْيُنٍ ),''aakhon ki thandakey, (thandak key asbaab) padha kartey they."
4329,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jannat ki baalisht bhar jagah, duniya sey aur is mein jo kuch hai us sab sey behtar hai."
4330,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jannat main eik koda rakhney ki jagah duniya aur is mein jo kuchh hai is sey behtar hai."
4331,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna , aap farma rahey they : jannat key sau darjey hain. har darja itna buland aur baala hai jitna aasman aur zamin key darmiyan fasla hai. sab sey buland jannat Al-Firdaus hai. jannat ka darmiyani (ya aa'laa tareen) maqam firdous hai. Arshe-Ilaahii firdous par hai. usi sey jannat ki nehren phoot'ti hain, isliye tum jab Allah sey maango to jannatul-Firdaus manga karo."
4332,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik din Rasool lillah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum sey farmaya : kya koi hai jo husoole-jannat key liye kamar kas ley? kyonkey jannat ki koi misal nahin. Kaba ke  Rab ki qism ! is main to jag-mag karta Noor hai, lehlehaatey huye khushbudar paudey hain, mazbut (aur buland aur baala) mehal hain, behti nehren hain, pakkey huye be-shumar phal hain, Haseen aur Jameel (khoobsurat) biwi hai, kapdon key bahut sey jodey hain, jahan buland aur baala, mehfooz aur dilkash gharon mein, hamesha nematon aur khushiyon mein rehna hai. haazirin ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! hum uskey liye tayyari kerengey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kaho : Insha-Allah. phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jihad ka zikr farmaya aur uski targheeb dilai."
4333,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jannat mein jo giroh sab sey pehley dakhil hoga, un ki shaklen chaudahwin key chaand ki tarah (khoobsurat) hongi. unkey baad dakhil honey waley itney roshan hongey jaisey aasman mein sab sey ziyada chamakney wala roshan sitaara. unhein na peshab ki hajat hogi, na pakhaney ki, na naak sinkeingey. aur na thookengey. un ki kanghiyaan soney ki, unka paseena kastoori (ki tarah khushbudar) hoga. un ki angeethiyon mein (jalaaney key liye) ood ki (khushbudar) lakdi hogi. un ki biwiyan moti aakhon wali hooren hongi. un ki aadaat eik aadmi ki aadaat ki tarah (eik doosrey sey mushabeh) hongi. wo apney walid Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam) ki shakal aur surat par (qad mein) saath saath key hongey.Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney Abu-Muaawia an al-Aamash an Abi Saleh key wastey sey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) hi sey, ibne Fuzel an Imaara ki riwayat ki tarah riwayat bayan ki hai."
4334,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Kausar jannat main eik nehar hai. uskey kinarey soney key hain. wo yaqut aur motiyon par behti hai. uski mitti kastoori sey ziyada umda aur uska pani shehad sey ziyada mitha aur barf sey ziyada safed hai."
4335,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jannat main eik darkht hai jis key saye main eik sawar sau saal tak chalta rahega tab bhi saya khatam nahin hoga. chaho to ye aayat padh lo ( وَظِلٍّ مَّمْدُودٍ ),''aur lambey lambey sayon mein.''"
4336,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke un ki mulaqat Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey hui to Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main Allah sey dua karta hun ke wo mujhey aur aap ko jannat key bazar mein jama kerey. Hazrat Saeed (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : kya jannat mein bhi bazar hoga? farmaya : haan , mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bataya : jannati jab jannat mein dakhil ho jaeyngey to apney aamal key mutabiq (apney apney darjey mein) thehrengey. unhein duniya key dino key andazey key mutabiq Jume key din ijazat di jaeygi to wo Allah ki ziyaarat kerengey. wo unkey liye apna arsh zahir kerega aur khud bhi jannat key baghaat mein sey eik baagh mein zuhoor farmaeyga. unkey liye Noor key member rakhey jaeyngey aur moti key member, yaqut key member, zamarrud key member, soney key member aur chaandi key member (rakhey jaaeyngey). un mein sey kam darjey key momin, un mein sey koi haqeer nahin hoga, kastoori aur kaafur key tilon par betheingey. unhein yun mehsus hoga ke kursiyon waley un sey aa'laa nashiston par nahin. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kya hum apney Rab ki ziyaarat kerengey? aap ney farmaya : haan , kya tumhein suraj ko ya chaudahwin raat key chaand ko dekhney mein shak hota hai? hamney kaha : nahin . aap ney farmaya : is tarah tumhein apney Rab key deedar mein koi shak nahin hoga . Allah Taala majlis key har shakhs sey mukhatib ho kar baat cheet farmaeyga. Allah Taala tum mein sey eik aadmi sey farmaeyga : aey falan ! kya tujhey yad nahin jis din tu ney falan falan kaam kiya tha? yani Allah Taala bandey ki baaz dunyawi ghaltiyaan yad karaaeyga. banda kaheyga : merey Rab ! kya tu ney mujhey bakhsh nahin diya? Allah Taala farmaeyga : kyon nahin? meri bakhshish ki wusat hi ki wajeh sey to to is maqam par pahuncha hai. isi beech mein unkey ooper eik badal chha jaaeyga. us sey un par aisi khushbu barseygi ke us jaisi mehak unhoney kabhi na soonghi hogi. phir Allah Taala farmaeyga : utho , mainey tumhaari izzat afzaai key liye jo kuchh tayyar kiya hai is mein sey jo chaho ley lo. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tab hum eik bazar mein jaaeyngey jisey farishton ney gher rakha hoga. is mein aisi cheezen hongi jaisi aakhon ney kabhi nahin dekhi, na kanon ney suni aur na dilon mein unka khayal aaya. farmaya : hum jo chahengey, (khaadim) hamarey liye uthaeyngey. us bazar mein na koi chiz bechi jaaeygi na khareedi jaaeygi. us bazar mein jannati eik doosrey sey mulaqat kerengey. eik buland darjey wala aadmi apney sey kam darjey waley ko milega aur un mein sey koi haqeer nahin hoga. wo (kam darjey wala) us (buland darjey waley) key libas ko dekh kar mutassir ho jaeyga lekin abhi uski baat khatam nahin hogi ke usey apna pehna huwa libas us sey behtar nazar aayega. uski wajeh ye hai ke wahan koi ghamgin nahin hoga. farmaya : phir hum apney gharon ko wapis aayengey to hamein hamari biwiyan milengi aur kahengi : khush aamadeed ! aap (ghar) aaye hain to aap key Husn aur khushbu mein rawangi key waqt ki nisbat izafa ho chuka hai. hum kahengey : aaj hum ko apney Rab Jabbaar ki hum nasheeni ka sharf hasil huwa hai, lihaza hamein isi andaz sey wapis aana tha jis shaan sey aaye hain."
4337,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala jisey bhi jannat mein dakhil karega, uski shaadi behtar biwiyon sey kar dega. do aurten hurain (jannat ki hooron) mein sey hongi aur sattar aurten wo hongi jo usey jahannamiyon ki virasat mili hogi. un mein sey har aurat ka maqam makhsus nihayat khoobsurat aur dilkash hoga aur mard ka uzu (khaas ang) aisa hoga jo naram nahin hoga. (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key ustad)  Hazrat Hisham bin Khalid (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : jahannamiyon ki virasat ka matlab ye hai ke jo mard jahannam mein jaaeyngey un ki aurten jannatiyon ko mil jaaeyngi, jaisey Firon ki biwi (jannati thi aur uska khawind jahannami isliye wo) virasat mein (kisi jannati ko) milegi."
4338,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin ko jannat mein jab bachchey ki khahish hogi to uski khahish key mutabiq eik ghadi mein (fauran) hamal, wiladat aur us bachchey ka bada hona (sab kuchh) ho jaaeyga."
4339,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey malum hai ke kon sa jahannami sab sey aakhir mein jahannam sey niklega aur kon sa jannati sab sey aakhir mein jannat mein dakhil hoga. eik aadmi jahannam sey ghutnon key bal ghisat'taa huwa niklega. usey kaha jaeyga : ja, jannat mein dakhil ho ja. wo aayega to usey mehsus hoga ke jannat bhari hui hai, chunanche wo wapis loteyga aur arz kerega : ya Rab ! wo to bhari hui hai. Allah Taala farmaeyga : ja, jannat mein dakhil ho ja. wo (dobara) aayega to usey mehsus hoga ke wo bhari hui hai. wo wapis ho jaaeyga aur arz kerega : merey Rab ! wo to bhari hui hai. Allah Paak farmaeyga : ja, jannat mein dakhil ho ja . wo aayega to usey mehsus hoga. ke wo bhari hui hai. wo phir ja kar arz kerega : merey Malik ! wo to bhari hui hai. Allah farmaeyga : ja, jannat mein dakhil ho ja. tujhey duniya key barabar aur (mazeed) us sey das guna jagah milegi. ya farmaya : tujhey duniya sey das-guna jagah milegi. banda kaheyga : kya to mujh sey mazaq karta ya mujh sey hanstaa hai, halanke to badshah hai? Sahaba farmatey hain : mainey dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khub hansey yahan tak key aap ki daadhein nazar aaney lagin. isliye kaha jata tha : ye shakhs sab sey kam darjey ka jannati hai."
4340,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala sey teen baar jannat maangta hai, jannat (uskey haq mein dua kartey huye) kehti hai : ya Allah ! isey jannat mein dakhil farma dey. aur jo koi teen baar (jahannam ki) aag sey panah maangta hai, jahannam (uskey haq mein dua kartey huye) kehti hai : ya Allah ! usey aag sey mehfooz farma."
4341,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey har eik key do ghar hain : eik ghar jannat mein aur eik ghar jahannam mein. jab koi shakhs faut ho kar jahannam mein jata hai to uska ghar virasat mein jannat walon ko mil jata hai. Allah Taala key is farman ka yehi matlab hai : (أُولَـٰئِكَ هُمُ الْوَارِثُونَ),''yehi log virasat pane-waley hain.''"
